*'''[[第三人称射击游戏|第三人称射击游戏类型]]'''：在游戏里只要能观看玩家控制角色、队友、敌友都属于广义上[[第三人称视角游戏|第三人称视角游戏]]，但严格上在游戏语术里说的第三人称射击游戏类型指的是以尾随镜头观看控制角色的第三人称视角游戏，因此玩家一般看到控制角色背面，而不是顶面、侧面。<ref>King, Geoff, etc (2006), Tomb Raiders and Space Invaders: Videogame Forms and Contexts p.98-99, I.B.Tauris, ISBN 978-1850438144.</ref><ref>Perry, David etc (2009), David Perry on Game Design: A Brainstorming ToolBox p.33-35, Charles River Media, ISBN 978-1584506683.</ref>由于早期[[2D|2D]]游戏的局限性这些游戏都是固定视角游戏，与[[第一人称射击游戏|第一人称射击游戏类型]]或FPS一样，第三人称射击游戏或TPS在早期发展史上都是非人物游戏类型，包括任天堂公司于1979年12月推出街机游戏《{{link-en|Radar Scope|Radar Scope}}》，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/do/feature?pager.offset=1&cId=3181467|title=Where Were They Then: The First Games of Nintendo, Konami, and More (Nintendo)|website=1up.com|accessdate=16 September 2017|archive-date=2012-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121017222352/http://www.1up.com/do/feature?pager.offset=1&cId=3181467|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>Stanton, Rich (2015), A Brief History Of Video Games: From Atari to Xbox One p.113-114, Robinson, ISBN 978-1472118806.</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.usgamer.net/articles/35-years-ago-nintendo-had-its-first-brush-with-video-game-disaster |title=35 Years Ago, Nintendo's First Brush With Video Disaster |access-date=2017-10-02 |archive-date=2019-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502051532/https://www.usgamer.net/articles/35-years-ago-nintendo-had-its-first-brush-with-video-game-disaster |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://whatculture.com/gaming/15-best-third-person-shooters-of-the-decade-so-far |title=15 Best Third-Person Shooters Of The Decade (So Far) |access-date=2017-10-02 |archive-date=2020-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200119055722/http://whatculture.com/gaming/15-best-third-person-shooters-of-the-decade-so-far |dead-url=no }}</ref>以尾随镜头观看的步行游戏为日本[[科乐美|科乐美]]公司于1987年2月20日推出的街机游戏《[[魂斗罗|魂斗罗]]》，但仅出现于部分场景，<ref name="hardcoregaming101">{{Cite web |url=http://www.hardcoregaming101.net/konamirunnguns/konamirunnguns.htm |title=Hardcore Gaming 101: Konami Run 'n Guns |access-date=2017-10-02 |archive-date=2017-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012212049/http://www.hardcoregaming101.net/konamirunnguns/konamirunnguns.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>其后全程采用尾随镜头观看的步行游戏为日本[[史克威尔|史克威尔]]公司于1987推出的《{{link-en|The 3-D Battles of WorldRunner|The 3-D Battles of WorldRunner}}》、<ref name=WorldRunner>{{Cite web |url=http://www.allgame.com/game.php?id=1136 |title=3-D WorldRunner - Overview - allgame |access-date=2014-11-14 |archive-date=2014-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141114120016/http://www.allgame.com/game.php?id=1136 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://nesguide.com/games/3d-battles-of-worldrunner/ |title=3-D Battles of World Runner, The (NES) - Acclaim, 1987 |access-date=2017-10-02 |archive-date=2019-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191006201250/http://nesguide.com/games/3d-battles-of-worldrunner/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>日本科乐美公司于1988推出的《{{link-en|餓流禍|Devastators}}》、<ref name="hardcoregaming101"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.uvlist.net/game-873-Devastators |title=Devastators |access-date=2017-09-30 |archive-date=2017-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170930180136/https://www.uvlist.net/game-873-Devastators |dead-url=no }}</ref>日本TAD公司于1988推出的《{{link-en|Cabal|Cabal (video game)}}》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.denofgeek.com/us/games/cabal/248774/cabal-the-80s-game-that-inspired-modern-third-person-shooters |title=Cabal: The 80s Game That Inspired Modern Third-Person Shooters |access-date=2017-09-30 |archive-date=2018-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180917144441/http://www.denofgeek.com/us/games/cabal/248774/cabal-the-80s-game-that-inspired-modern-third-person-shooters |dead-url=no }}</ref>等等。最早一批以自由视角的尾随镜头观看角色的射击游戏是任天堂公司于1993年2月21日推出的《[[星际火狐_(游戏)|星际火狐]]》<ref>Loguidice, Bill, etc (2009) Loguidice Vintage Games: An Insider Look at the History of Grand Theft Auto, Super Mario, and the Most Influential Games of All Time 1st Edition, Focal Press p.257, ISBN 978-0240811468.</ref><ref name="mattfox">Fox, Matt (2013), The Video Games Guide: 1,000+ Arcade, Console and Computer Games p.95-96, 287, 279, McFarland, ISBN 978-0786472574.</ref>和法国Delphine Software公司于1995年推出的步行游戏《{{link-en|Fade to Black|Fade to Black (video game)}}》，<ref name="denofgeek third">{{Cite web |url=http://www.denofgeek.com/games/12152/the-superiority-of-third-person-shooters |title=The superiority of third-person shooters |access-date=2017-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170930180809/http://www.denofgeek.com/games/12152/the-superiority-of-third-person-shooters |archive-date=2017-09-30 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://news.xbox.com/2015/10/09/games-know-your-genres-third-person-shooters/ |title=Know Your Genres: Third-Person Shooters - Xbox Wire |access-date=2017-10-07 |archive-date=2017-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171007170245/https://news.xbox.com/2015/10/09/games-know-your-genres-third-person-shooters/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://metro.co.uk/2013/10/10/flashback-psn-review-fade-to-black-4141452/ |title=Flashback PSN review – fade to black {{!}} Metro News |access-date=2017-10-07 |archive-date=2019-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190515104158/https://metro.co.uk/2013/10/10/flashback-psn-review-fade-to-black-4141452/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>这两款游戏都属于3D游戏。

*'''[[剧情画面|游戏剧情动画]]'''：剧情动画或cutscene最早由美国游戏设计师[[罗恩·吉伯特|罗恩·吉伯特]]于1987年定名。<ref name="GS-Fame">{{cite news|url=http://archive.gamespy.com/legacy/halloffame/mm.shtm|title=The GameSpy Hall of Fame|work=GameSpy|last1=Buecheler|first1=Christopher|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110311072453/http://archive.gamespy.com/legacy/halloffame/mm.shtm|archivedate=2011-03-11|accessdate=2017-10-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>最早一批在游戏加入剧情动画的游戏为[[街机游戏|街机游戏]]，包括日本太东公司于1979年9月推出的《{{link-en|太空侵略者2|List of Space Invaders video games}}》；<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.giantbomb.com/deluxe-space-invaders/3030-41053/ |title=Deluxe Space Invaders (Game) - Giant Bomb |access-date=2017-10-02 |archive-date=2020-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201103025333/https://www.giantbomb.com/deluxe-space-invaders/3030-41053/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Günzel, Stephan (2009), Conference Proceedings of The Philosophy of Computer Games 2008 p.115-116, Potsdam University Press, ISBN 978-3940793492.</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.progettoemma.net/gioco.php?&game=invadpt2&lang=en |title=Space Invaders Part II (Taito) - Progettoemma.net |access-date=2017-10-02 |archive-date=2017-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171003030204/http://www.progettoemma.net/gioco.php?&game=invadpt2&lang=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>任天堂公司于1979年10月推出的《{{link-en|Sheriff|Sheriff (video game)}}》；<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.giantbomb.com/sheriff/3030-27792/ |title=Sheriff (Game) - Giant Bomb |access-date=2017-10-02 |archive-date=2019-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190524093047/https://www.giantbomb.com/sheriff/3030-27792/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>日本[[南梦宫|南梦宫]]公司于1980年推出的《[[吃豆人|吃豆人]]》；<ref>Wolf, Mark J. P. (2012), Before the Crash: Early Video Game History p.131, Wayne State University Press, ISBN 978-0814334508.</ref><ref name="Mejia">Mejia, Robert, etc (2017), 100 Greatest Video Game Franchises p.40, Rowman & Littlefield Publishers, ISBN 978-1442278141.</ref>任天堂公司于1981年推出的《[[大金刚_(游戏)|大金刚]]》。<ref name="Mejia"/>最早的[[全动态影像|全动态影像]]的游戏剧情动画为日本[[Data_East|Data East]]公司于1983年推出的[[激光影碟|激光影碟]]游戏《Bega's Battle》。<ref>{{cite web|title=The Lives and Deaths of the Interactive Movie|first=Travis|last=Fahs|publisher=IGN|date=March 3, 2008|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2008/03/04/the-lives-and-deaths-of-the-interactive-movie?page=2|accessdate=2011-03-11|archive-date=2016-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160118024843/http://uk.ign.com/articles/2008/03/04/the-lives-and-deaths-of-the-interactive-movie?page=2|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sumonix.com/do-video-games-still-need-cutscenes |title=Do Video Games Still Need Cutscenes? {{!}} Sumonix |access-date=2017-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171003025745/http://sumonix.com/do-video-games-still-need-cutscenes |archive-date=2017-10-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>时间最长的游戏剧情动画为的日本科乐美公司于2008年6月12日推出的《[[合金装备4_爱国者之枪|合金装备4]]》，长达27分钟。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.houstonpress.com/arts/10-games-with-guinness-world-records-6392480 |title=10 Games With Guinness World Records {{!}} Houston Press |access-date=2017-10-02 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126142509/https://www.houstonpress.com/arts/10-games-with-guinness-world-records-6392480 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

