rchive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171008234136/http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/first-console-game-to-use-stealth|dead-url=no}}</ref>美国{{link-en|Muse Software|Muse Software}}公司于1981年推出的电脑游戏《[[德军总部|德军总部]]》也属于早期的潜行游戏类型。<ref name="gamesradarstealth">{{cite web|title=The sneaky history of stealth games: Hide and seek through the ages|author=Shane Patterson|publisher=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]|date=February 3, 2009|url=http://www.gamesradar.com/the-sneaky-history-of-stealth-games/|accessdate=2009-06-21|archive-date=2012-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120523181200/http://www.gamesradar.com/the-sneaky-history-of-stealth-games/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在进入3D游戏时代之前比较知名的潜行游戏类型为《{{link-en|超越德军总部|Beyond Castle Wolfenstein}}》(1984年)、<ref>Bogdan, Purcaru Ion (2014), Games vs. Hardware. The History of PC Gaming. The 80's p.262.</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://kotaku.com/5817303/in-memory-of-the-original-castle-wolfenstein-the-one-that-wasnt-in-3d |title=In Memory of the Original Castle Wolfenstein (the one That Wasn't In 3D) |access-date=2017-10-08 |archive-date=2018-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181108161315/https://kotaku.com/5817303/in-memory-of-the-original-castle-wolfenstein-the-one-that-wasnt-in-3d |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=gamingtarget>{{cite web|title=The Unseen History of the Stealth Game|author=Jason Cisarano|publisher=Gaming Target|date=April 11, 2007|url=http://www.gamingtarget.com/article.php?artid=6786&gameid=2481|accessdate=2009-08-27|archive-date=2008-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081009191057/http://www.gamingtarget.com/article.php?artid=6786&gameid=2481|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[合金装备_(1987年游戏)|合金装备]]》(1987年)<ref name="gamesradarstealth"/>等等；进入3D游戏时代，比较知名的潜行游戏类型为《[[天诛|天诛]]》(1998年)、<ref name="nytimes">{{cite web|url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9C04E0DA1139F937A15755C0A9629C8B63&sec=&spon=&pagewanted=all|title=GAME THEORY; First Use Your Brain, Then Unleash Your Brawn|author=Charles Herold|date=2004-06-24|publisher=New York Times}}</ref><ref name="maxpc0408">{{cite book|publisher=Maximum PC|date=August 2004|title=PCs and Consoles: Unlikely Bedfellows?|author=Thomas L. McDonald}}</ref>《[[神偷：暗黑计划|神偷]]》(1998年)、<ref name="nytimes"/>《[[杀手：代号47|杀手：代号47]]》(2000年)、<ref name="gamesradarstealth"/><ref name="deadlyshadows">{{cite web|url=http://pc.ign.com/articles/518/518951p1.html|title=Thief: Deadly Shadows Review|author=Tom McNamara|date=2004-05-25|publisher=IGN|accessdate=2009-03-16|archive-date=2004-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040624214306/http://pc.ign.com/articles/518/518951p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[刺客教條_(遊戲)|刺客信条]]》(2007年)<ref>{{cite book|publisher=GameAxis Unwired|date=September 2007|title=Review of Assassin's Creed}}</ref>等等。一些3D第三人称射击游戏，例如《[[古墓丽影_(2013年游戏)|古墓丽影]]》(2013年)、<ref name="kotaku">{{Cite web |url=https://www.kotaku.com.au/2013/03/tomb-raider-vs-uncharted-the-comparison-we-had-to-make/ |title=Tomb Raider Vs. Uncharted: The Comparison We Had To Make {{!}} Kotaku Australia |access-date=2017-10-08 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124033029/https://www.kotaku.com.au/2013/03/tomb-raider-vs-uncharted-the-comparison-we-had-to-make/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>《[[神秘海域：德雷克船长的宝藏|神秘海域]]》(2007年)<ref name="kotaku"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2007/11/uncharted-review/ |title=Finding a bride in a brothel: a review of Uncharted {{!}} Ars Technica |access-date=2017-10-08 |archive-date=2020-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200811134617/https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2007/11/uncharted-review/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="gamesradarstealthattack">{{Cite web |url=http://www.gamesradar.com/how-last-us-finally-fixed-longstanding-problems-uncharted/ |title=How The Last of Us finally fixed the longstanding problems of Uncharted {{!}} GamesRadar+ |access-date=2017-10-08 |archive-date=2017-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171231192935/http: