web.com/rc760/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[美能达|美能达]]Maxxum 7000和9000 (1985年) 、<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/1986/10/05/arts/camera-at-photokina-still-video-cameras.html |title=CAMERA; At Photokina, Still-Video Cameras |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2017-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924095616/http://www.nytimes.com/1986/10/05/arts/camera-at-photokina-still-video-cameras.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>启能CP9-AF (1988年) 、<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.butkus.org/chinon/chinon/cp9-af-extra/cp-9-extra.htm |title=CHINON'S CP9-AF AUTOFOCUS SLR TO HAVE A VIDEO BACK |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2019-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190729102848/https://www.butkus.org/chinon/chinon/cp9-af-extra/cp-9-extra.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>尼康SVC (1986年) 、<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nikonweb.com/svc/ |title=Nikon Still Video Camera (prototype) |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111202710/http://www.nikonweb.com/svc/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>QV-1000C (1988年) ，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nikonweb.com/qv1000c/ |title=Nikon QV-1000C: The history of Nikon's first electronic camera |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2020-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200222134059/http://www.nikonweb.com/qv1000c/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>都以2英寸的磁盘作为存储媒介，省去了在更换胶卷时导致底片彻底[[感光度|曝光]]的不方便麻烦。<ref name="Takiff">{{Cite web |url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1987-11-06/entertainment/8703250104_1_casio-disc-auto-exposure-control |title=Casio Focuses On Consumer With Still-frame Camera-player November 06, 1987 |access-date=2013-07-24 |archive-date=2017-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924095903/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1987-11-06/entertainment/8703250104_1_casio-disc-auto-exposure-control |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*'''[[智能手表|电视手表]]'''：日本[[愛普生|愛普生]]公司于1982年7月16日或9月23日推出全球第一款液晶显示屏电视手表T001，带有1.2英寸的单色液晶显示屏，同时它还配有耳机和一个大小与索尼[[Walkman|Walkman]]类似的可携带的电视接收器TR02-01，拨动接收器上的转换轮可以观看或收听选者的节目或电台。手表有两个屏幕，位于顶部的狭窄屏幕用于显示时间、日历以及闹钟功能，而下面的蓝色屏幕则用来显示影像，这款手表被堪称为[[智能手表|智能手表]]始祖。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://museum.syssrc.com/artifact/mobile/900/ |title=Seiko TV Watch |access-date=2017-09-24 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108131745/https://museum.syssrc.com/artifact/mobile/900/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://monochrome-watches.com/seiko-t001-mother-smart-watches/ |title=The Seiko T001 – Mother Of All Smart Watches |access-date=2017-09-24 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112020600/https://monochrome-watches.com/seiko-t001-mother-smart-watches/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*'''[[智能手表|计算机手表、触摸屏手表]]'''：日本[[愛普生|愛普生]]公司分别于1983年和1984年推出全球第一款配有物理键盘的手表、第一款计算机式手表Data-2000和UC-2000，两款手表都带有可拆组的外接全键盘扩展坞，通过无线方式链接，拥有能够存储2000字符容量的备忘录功能，为智能手表史上的重要里程碑，该公司于1984年至1985年又推出类似产品UC-3000和Memo Diary。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mobileindustryreview.com/2016/10/33860.html |title=The History of the: Smartwatch |access-date=2017-09-24 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111203502/https://www.mobileindustryreview.com/2016/10/33860.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://pocketcalculatorshow.com/nerdwatch/seiko-computer-watch-fun/ |title=Seiko Computer Watch Fun |access-date=2017-09-24 |archive-date=2012-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024235156/http://pocketcalculatorshow.com/nerdwatch/seiko-computer-watch-fun/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://gizmodo.com/5401391/the-seiko-uc-2000-wrist-pc-an-awkward-80s-attempt-to-live-the-cyborg-life |title=The Seiko UC-2000 Wrist PC: An Awkward '80s Attempt To Live The Cyborg Life |access-date=2017-09-24 |archive-date=2017-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171226044929/https://gizmodo.com/5401391/the-seiko-uc-2000-wrist-pc-an-awkward-80s-attempt-to-live-the-cyborg-life |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.seikodigitalwatches.com/SEIKO2.htm |title=Seiko Wrist Computer Watches, Seiko Memo Dairy Watches |access-date=2017-09-24 |archive-date=2017-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924093318/http://www.seikodigitalwatches.com/SEIKO2.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>愛普生公司于1985年推出全球第一款搭载处理器的手表、第一款可运行计算机应用的手表、第一款配有触摸屏的手表RC-20，它具有[[Zilog_Z80|Zilog Z80]] 8位微处理器，8K的ROM和2K的RAM，该产品没有按键，使用触摸屏，通过RS-232C电缆可链接至[[IBM_PC|IBM PC]]、{{link-en|IBM PCjr|IBM PCjr}}、[[Apple_IIc|Apple IIc]]和{{link-en|Apple IIe|Apple IIe}}电脑。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.watchesnsuch.net/personal_computer_influence_on_smartwatches_1980s.html |title=Personal Computer Influence on Smartwatches (1980s) |access-date=2017-09-24 |archive-date=2020-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200216104053/http://watchesnsuch.net/personal_computer_influence_on_smartwatches_1980s.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.pcworld.com/article/2028545/evolution-of-the-smartwatch.html#slide6 |title=Evolution of the smartwatch |access-date=2017-09-24 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111223837/https://www.pcworld.com/article/2028545/evolution-of-the-smartwatch.html#slide6 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*'''[[笔记本电脑|笔记本电脑]]'''：[[爱普生|爱普生]]公司于1981年11月18日在[[拉斯维加斯|拉斯维加斯]]的[[COMDEX|COMDEX]]展览会上发布了一款采用液晶显示器及带有内置蓄电池的笔记本电脑{{link-en|HC-20|HX-20}}，该笔记本在北美销售型号为HX-20，由爱普生公司员工横澤由紀夫于1980年7月设计出。<ref>[http://www.xtimeline.com/evt/view.aspx?id=360286 The Espon HX-20 1981]{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.atarimagazines.com/creative/v9n3/101_Epson_HX20_computer.php |title=Epson HX-20 computer |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2020-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808174711/https://www.atarimagazines.com/creative/v9n3/101_Epson_HX20_computer.php |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.motobayashi.net/interop/comdex.html |title=COMDEX History |access-date=2017-09-16 |archive-date=2018-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224204252/http://motobayashi.net/interop/comdex.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="hx20">[http://oldcomputers.net/hx-20.html Epson HX-20] {{Wayback|url=http://oldcomputers.net/hx-20.html |date=20210127080552 }}, Old Computers</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://patents.google.com/patent/FR2487094A1/en |title=FR2487094A1 patent: Notebook computer system small |access-date=2017-09-16 |archive-date=2020-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200307025424/https://patents.google.com/patent/FR2487094A1/en |dead-url=no }}</ref>HX-20是广泛承认的世界上第一台真正的笔记本电脑，其重量仅有1.6公斤，而且内建可续航50小时的镍镉电池。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://invent.answers.com/technology/5-facts-about-the-worlds-first-laptop-computer |title=5 Facts About the World's First Laptop Computer |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2013-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131211071914/http://invent.answers.com/technology/5-facts-about-the-worlds-first-laptop-computer |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/2012/feb/26/first-computers-john-von-neumann |title=The true fathers of computing |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2013-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130116183821/http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/2012/feb/26/first-computers-john-von-neumann |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://driverfinderpro.com/driver-guide/epson-drivers/ |title=Epson Drivers |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2020-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929101632/https://driverfinderpro.com/driver-guide/epson-drivers/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.atarimagazines.com/creative/v10n1/38_14_notebook_computers_in_.php |title=14 Notebook Computers in Brief  |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2017-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171220174547/https://www.atarimagazines.com/creative/v10n1/38_14_notebook_computers_in_.php |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Tony">{{Cite web |url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2012/11/02/a_history_of_computing_in_20_objects_part_two/page2.html |title=A history of personal computing in 20 objects part 2 |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2012-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121226164725/http://www.theregister.co.uk/2012/11/02/a_history_of_computing_in_20_objects_part_two/page2.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=epman>{{Cite web |url=http://files.support.epson.com/pdf/hx20__/hx20__u1.pdf |title=HX-20 Operations Manual |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2020-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200120033154/http://files.support.epson.com/pdf/hx20__/hx20__u1.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>同年4月3日美国Osborne计算机公司也推出了Osborne 1，不过该计算机使用CRT显示器，没有内置电池，其体积庞大，重达10.7公斤，不容易携带。<ref name="Tony"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2383022,00.asp |title=First Portable Computer Debuted 30 Years Ago |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2017-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170916225554/https://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2383022,00.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>第一台翻盖型专业笔记本是1982年美国Grid Systems公司推出的GRiD Compass 1101，重量5公斤，但由于售价太高，只有一些政府单位、军队、以及太空总署的太空任务得以使用。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://oldcomputers.net/grid1101.html |title=GRiD Compass 1101 |access-date=2013-07-17 |archive-date=2008-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080916202158/http://oldcomputers.net/grid1101.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Lupton, Ellen (2014), Beautiful Users: Designing for People p.28. ISBN 1616892919.</ref>东芝也遂在1985年11月推出了9英寸液晶单色显示屏T1100笔记本电脑，T1100被认为是世界首台广泛销售于市场的笔记本电脑。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tablet-news.com/2010/06/22/toshiba-celebrates-25-years-of-mass-market-laptops-launches-worlds-first-dual-screen-laptop-libretto-w100/ |title=Toshiba Celebrates 25 Years of Mass Market Laptops, Launches World’s First Dual Screen Laptop: Libretto W100 |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2016-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160616203025/http://tablet-news.com/2010/06/22/toshiba-celebrates-25-years-of-mass-market-laptops-launches-worlds-first-dual-screen-laptop-libretto-w100/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20050420005391/en/Toshiba-Celebrates-20th-Anniversary-Mass-Market-Notebook-Computer |title=Toshiba Celebrates 20th Anniversary of First Mass-Market Notebook Computer; Introduced in 1985, Toshiba T1100 Weighed Nine Pounds and Heralded New Era of Mobile Computing Innovation that Continues Today |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2017-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170916140926/http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20050420005391/en/Toshiba-Celebrates-20th-Anniversary-Mass-Market-Notebook-Computer |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://lowendmac.com/1984/macintosh-128k/ |title=Mac 128K |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2020-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127014335/https://lowendmac.com/1984/macintosh-128k/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*'''[[软盘|3.5英寸软盘]]'''：1981年索尼首次发布3.5英寸软盘，1982年世界上第一台使用3.5英寸软驱的电脑是索尼SMC 70，<ref name="smc70">{{Cite web |url=http://www.old-computers.com/museum/computer.asp?c=362 |title=Sony SMC70 |access-date=2013-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130703032649/http://www.old-computers.com/museum/computer.asp?c=362 |archive-date=2013-07-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>[[蘋果公司|苹果公司]]1984年1月24日推出的Macintosh 128K也首次使用3.5英寸软驱。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://oldcomputers.net/macintosh.html |title=Macintosh 1984 |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2021-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127080809/http://oldcomputers.net/macintosh.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.macgeek.org/museum/sony400kdrive/ |title=SONY Micro Floppydisk Drive - Model OA-D30V |access-date=2013-07-16 |archive-date=2021-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111132730/http://www.macgeek.org/museum/sony400kdrive/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>3.5英寸软盘随后成为主流和最影响力的软盘格式，取代了市场上主流的5.25.英寸软盘及2英寸、2.5英寸、3英寸软盘。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/1983/02/23/business/company-news-second-group-sets-floppy-disk-plans.html |title=COMPANY NEWS; Second Group Sets Floppy Disk Plans |access-date=2013-07-16 |archive-date=2017-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171007171009/http://www.nytimes.com/1983/02/23/business/company-news-second-group-sets-floppy-disk-plans.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theinquirer.net/inquirer/news/1602720/sony-announces-death-floppy-disk |title=Sony announces the death of the floppy disk  |access-date=2013-07-16 |archive-date=2019-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191225045841/https://www.theinquirer.net/inquirer/news/1602720/sony-announces-death-floppy-disk |dead-url=no }}</ref>软盘标志甚至成为许多软件，例如[[Microsoft_Office|Office]]的储存图标。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.zdnet.com/blog/hardware/the-floppy-disk-save-icon-kill-it-with-fire/16958 |title=The floppy disk save icon - Kill it with fire! |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2014-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408051313/http://www.zdnet.com/blog/hardware/the-floppy-disk-save-icon-kill-it-with-fire/16958 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lifehacker.com.au/2012/08/why-is-the-save-icon-still-a-floppy-disk/ |title=Why Is The Save Icon Still A Floppy Disk? |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125070717/https://www.lifehacker.com.au/2012/08/why-is-the-save-icon-still-a-floppy-disk/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*'''2英寸软盘'''：2英寸软盘俗称Video Floppy，简称VF，第一批最早的2英寸软盘是索尼为了配合单反相机Mavica在1981年推出的存储媒介Mavipack，随后又陆续推出2.0版本Hi-VF。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.videointerchange.com/video-history.htm |title=Video History |access-date=2013-07-24 |archive-date=2014-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201222648/http://www.videointerchange.com/video-history.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>在80年代和90年代初各厂牌都为自己的摄像机、相机、单反相机推出可多次擦写的2英寸软盘作为存储媒介，每片售价6-10美元，<ref name="Takiff"/>美国[[天顶电子|天顶电子]]于1989年推出的小型笔记本Minisport也采用日本富士LT-1的2英寸软盘。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://oldcomputers.net/zenith-minisport.html |title=Zenith MinisPort |access-date=2013-07-24 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109200315/http://oldcomputers.net/zenith-minisport.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.pcmag.com/slideshow/story/262600/ten-strange-pc-storage-formats/1 |title=2-Inch Floppy Disk |access-date=2013-07-24 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304125516/http://www.pcmag.com/slideshow/story/262600/ten-strange-pc-storage-formats/1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*'''[[十字键|D-pad]]'''：D-pad的雏形在任天堂十字键出现以前在日本的两款[[街机游戏|街机游戏]]上就已经出现，日本{{link-en|UPL|UPL}}公司于1976年推出的《{{link-en|Blockade|Blockade (video game)}}》游戏以及日本[[SNK|SNK]]公司于1981年推出《[[Vanguard|Vanguard]]》街机游戏就有由四个方向的圆形按键组成的类似十字键的操控界面；<ref>Arcade Museum [https://www.arcade-museum.com/game_detail.php?game_id=7160 Blockade] {{Wayback|url=https://www.arcade-museum.com/game_detail.php?game_id=7160 |date=20210125222938 }}, [https://www.arcade-museum.com/game_detail.php?game_id=10293 Vanguard] {{Wayback|url=https://www.arcade-museum.com/game_detail.php?game_id=10293 |date=20201004155754 }}</ref><ref>Matt Barton & Bill Loguidice, [http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/4099/the_history_of_robotron_2084__.php?page=2 The History of Robotron: 2084 - Running Away While Defending Humanoids] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/4099/the_history_of_robotron_2084__.php?page=2 |date=20190502003947 }}, [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]</ref>但真正的十字键由任天堂发明，1982年6月3日任天堂的开发部部长横井军平推出了日后被称为“D-Pad”的操控界面的十字键的[[掌上游戏机|掌上游戏机]]，由四方向移动的扁平十字形按键组成，D-pad最早出现在[[Game_&_Watch|Game & Watch]]掌上游戏机系列的DK-52《[[大金剛系列|大金刚]]》游戏。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.digitalgamemuseum.org/consolecontrollerevolution/d-pad/ |title=Evolution of the Console Controller – The D-Pad Era |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2020-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001035728/https://www.digitalgamemuseum.org/consolecontrollerevolution/d-pad/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="IGN">{{cite web| last = Buchanan| first = Levi| title = From Janitor to Superstar Gunpei Yokoi, inventor of the Game Boy, would have been 67 this week.| publisher = [[IGN|IGN]]| date = 2008-09-08| url = http://retro.ign.com/articles/908/908569p1.html| accessdate = 2008-12-28| archive-date = 2012-04-20| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120420091221/http://retro.ign.com/articles/908/908569p1.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>早期的游戏主机[[游戏控制器|游戏控制器]]都以小旋轮、摇杆为主，D-pad随后成为[[手柄|游戏手柄]]的主流，包括[[微软|微软]]的[[Xbox|Xbox]]在内。

*'''[[第三人称射击游戏|越肩视角游戏类型]]'''：{{link-en|越肩视角|Over the shoulder shot}}属于第三人称视角游戏类型的衍生板，以尾随镜头观看，特点是镜头在后方肩上，因此只能看到控制人物角色的膝盖或腰以上，越肩视角游戏类型不特指射击游戏。<ref>Lecky-Thompson, Guy W. (2007), Video Game Design Revealed, Charles River Media p.35-6, 199, ISBN 978-1584505624.</ref><ref>Strauven, Wanda (2007), The Cinema of Attractions Reloaded p.303-305, Amsterdam University Press, ISBN 978-9053569443.</ref>越肩视角游戏类型在早期发展史上的游戏都是[[格斗游戏|格斗游戏]]，包括任天堂公司于1983年推出的《[[拳無虛發_(1983年遊戲)|拳无虚发]]》、<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arcade-museum.com/game_detail.php?game_id=9155 |title=Punch-Out!! - Videogame by Nintendo |access-date=2017-10-02 |archive-date=2019-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190925193739/https://www.arcade-museum.com/game_detail.php?game_id=9155 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.giantbomb.com/punch-out/3030-27410/ |title=Punch-Out!! (Game) - Giant Bomb |access-date=2017-09-30 |archive-date=2017-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170930180210/https://www.giantbomb.com/punch-out/3030-27410/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>日本[[ADK_(遊戲公司)|ADK]]公司于1990年推出的《{{link-en|Crossed Swords|Crossed Swords (video game)}}》、<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.platoscavern.com/crossed-swords-arcade-review |title=Crossed Swords (Arcade) Review |access-date=2017-10-02 |archive-date=2017-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171003030732/http://www.platoscavern.com/crossed-swords-arcade-review |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.engadget.com/2009/08/12/interview-ghostfire-games-ed-roman-on-rage-of-the-gladiator/ |title=Interview: Ghostfire Games' Ed Roman on Rage of the Gladiator |access-date=2017-10-02 |archive-date=2017-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171003075148/https://www.engadget.com/2009/08/12/interview-ghostfire-games-ed-roman-on-rage-of-the-gladiator/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>日本[[万普|万普]]公司于1993年推出的《Dragon Ball Z V.R.V.S》<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.arcade-museum.com/game_detail.php?game_id=7637 |title=Dragon Ball Z V.R. V.S. - Videogame by Banpresto and Sega |access-date=2017-10-02 |archive-date=2019-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190325031352/https://www.arcade-museum.com/game_detail.php?game_id=7637 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.vandal.net/noticia/1350694167/verano-de-dragon-ball-dragon-ball-z-vrvs/ |title=Verano de Dragon Ball: Dragon Ball Z: V.R.V.S. - Vandal |access-date=2017-10-02 |archive-date=2017-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171003075124/http://www.vandal.net/noticia/1350694167/verano-de-dragon-ball-dragon-ball-z-vrvs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>等等。法国[[育碧蒙特利尔|育碧蒙特利尔]]公司于2002年11月12日推出的《[[Splinter_Cell|Splinter Cell]]》是最早以越肩视角来切换瞄射模式的人物射击游戏之一，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/e3-2002-splinter-cell-preshow-report/1100-2866895/ |title=E3 2002: Splinter Cell preshow report |access-date=2017-09-30 |archive-date=2017-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170930175651/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/e3-2002-splinter-cell-preshow-report/1100-2866895/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>而最早的全程采用越肩视角的人物射击游戏，包括不在切换模式下、以及切换模式后以越肩视角观看人物角色的游戏为日本[[卡普空|卡普空]]公司于2005年1月11日推出的《[[生化危机4|生化危机4]]》。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://kotaku.com/resident-evil-4-changed-action-games-forever-1786901886 |title=Resident Evil 4 Changed Action Games Forever |access-date=2017-09-30 |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930231804/https://kotaku.com/resident-evil-4-changed-action-games-forever-1786901886 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*'''[[恐怖游戏|恐怖游戏类型]]'''：最早的恐怖游戏是日本太东公司员工滝口明和三橋正幸设计的《AX-2: Uchuu Yusousen Nostromo》，这款科幻恐怖电脑游戏受到了另一款日本[[隐蔽类游戏|隐蔽类游戏]]《Manbiki Shoujo》(1980年) 和美国电影《[[异形_(电影)|异形]]》(1979年) 所启发，被认为是最早的恐怖游戏类型，于1981年被日本[[ASCII_(公司)|ASCII]]公司发行。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://whatculture.com/gaming/10-firsts-that-changed-video-games-forever?page=11 |title=10 "Firsts" That Changed Video Games Forever |access-date=2017-10-01 |archive-date=2018-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180927062549/http://whatculture.com/gaming/10-firsts-that-changed-video-games-forever?page=11 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last=Szczepaniak |first=John |year=2014 |title=The Untold History of Japanese Game Developers |publisher=SMG Szczepaniak |volume=1 |pages=544–573 |isbn=978-0-9929260-3-8 }}</ref>美国[[雅達利|雅達利]]公司于1981年12月31日推出的《{{link-en|Haunted House|Haunted House (video game)}}》也属于早期的恐怖游戏。<ref name="fear101">{{cite web | url = http://retro.ign.com/articles/880/880202p1.html | title = Fear 101: A Beginner's Guide to Survival Horror | publisher = [[IGN|IGN]] | author = Jim Sterling | date = 2008-06-09 | accessdate = 2009-04-17 | archive-date = 2012-02-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120217164343/http://retro.ign.com/articles/880/880202p1.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>最为知名的早期恐怖游戏为日本[[卡普空|卡普空]]公司于1989年12月15日推出的《{{link-en|Sweet Home|Sweet Home (video game)}}》部分影响了该公司于1996年3月22日推出的《[[生化危机_(1996年游戏)|生化危机]]》，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hardcoregaming101.net/sweethome/sweethome.htm |title=Sweet Home - Famicom (1989) |access-date=2017-10-01 |archive-date=2018-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180322105425/http://www.hardcoregaming101.net/sweethome/sweethome.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>不过《生化危机》里固定镜头的机位摆放释出的电影效果则是受到了法国[[英宝格|英宝格]]公司于1992年推出的《[[鬼屋魔影_(1992年游戏)|鬼屋魔影]]》影响。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/scitech/technology/377445/watch-horror-classic-alone-in-the-dark-gets-reboot-trailer/story/ |title=WATCH: Horror classic ‘Alone in the Dark’ gets reboot trailer |access-date=2017-10-01 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112003638/https://www.gmanetwork.com/news/scitech/technology/377445/watch-horror-classic-alone-in-the-dark-gets-reboot-trailer/story/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="gamespot-mikami">[http://www.gamespot.com/articles/resident-evil-creator-shinji-mikami-reflects-on-th/1100-6435918/ Resident Evil Creator Shinji Mikami Reflects on the Series' Roots] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/resident-evil-creator-shinji-mikami-reflects-on-th/1100-6435918/ |date=20160801212914 }}, [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] (March 22, 2016)</ref>

*'''[[平台游戏|平台游戏类型]]'''：在2D游戏时代平台游戏类型为[[横向卷轴游戏|横向卷轴游戏]]。最早的平台游戏类型为日本{{link-en|UPL|UPL}}公司于1980年11月推出的街机游戏《{{link-en|Space Panic|Space Panic}}》；<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.retrogamesnow.co.uk/space-panic-arcade-game-by-universal/ |title=Space Panic Arcade Game by Universal - Retro Games Now! |access-date=2017-10-02 |archive-date=2018-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226063555/https://www.retrogamesnow.co.uk/space-panic-arcade-game-by-universal/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.gamespot.com/space-panic/ |title=Space Panic - GameSpot |access-date=2017-10-02 |archive-date=2019-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190323024706/https://www.gamespot.com/space-panic/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>最早在不同平台间进行跳跃、翻过障碍物的平台游戏类型为任天堂公司于1981年7月9日推出的街机游戏《[[大金刚_(游戏)|大金刚]]》；<ref name="mattfox"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/donkey-kong-video-game-still-going-strong-over-30-years-later/ |title="Donkey Kong" video game celebrates birthday still going strong - CBS News |access-date=2017-10-02 |archive-date=2017-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171003120525/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/donkey-kong-video-game-still-going-strong-over-30-years-later/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>最早的横向卷轴的平台射击游戏类型为日本ADK公司在北美于1981年推出的街机游戏《{{link-en|Jump Bug|Jump Bug}}》。<ref name="Leif Ericson Awards">[http://retro.ign.com/articles/861/861550p2.html IGN: The Leif Ericson Awards] {{Wayback|url=http://retro.ign.com/articles/861/861550p2.html |date=20120309041726 }}, [[IGN|IGN]]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.gamespot.com/jump-bug/ |title=Jump Bug - GameSpot |access-date=2017-10-03 |archive-date=2019-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190219201442/https://www.gamespot.com/jump-bug/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在进入3D游戏时代之前比较知名的横向卷轴的平台游戏类型为《[[超级马里奥兄弟|超级马里奥兄弟]]》(1985年)、《[[洛克人_(游戏)|洛克人]]》(1987年)、《[[刺猬索尼克_(1991年游戏)|索尼克]]》(1991年) 等等。进入3D游戏时代，平台游戏类型在游戏主机和电脑上已经很罕见，比较知名的为《[[超级马里奥64|超级马里奥64]]》(1996年6月)、《[[古惑狼|古惑狼]]》(1996年9月) 等等，但一般以3D第三人称射击游戏出现，例如《[[古墓丽影_(1996年游戏)|古墓丽影]]》(1996年)、<ref name="mattfox"/><ref>Darley, Andrew (2000), Visual Digital Culture: Surface Play and Spectacle in New Media Genres p.204, Routledge, ISBN 978-0415165556.</ref>《[[神秘海域：德雷克船长的宝藏|神秘海域]]》(2007年) 等等；<ref>Despain, Wendy, Writing for Video Game Genres: From FPS to RPG p.39-43, A K Peters/CRC Press, ISBN 978-1568814179.</ref>随着智能手机平台的兴起，很多游戏公司开始推出平台游戏类型，一部分为无线跑步平台游戏，平台游戏在制作上节约，适合智能手机的较低性能以及触屏上的单键控制。<ref>Unger, Kimberly (2011), Game Development Essentials: Mobile Game Development, Cengage Learning p.89, ISBN 978-1418052652.</ref><ref>Rettig, Pascal (2012), Professional HTML5 Mobile Game Development p.349, Wrox, ISBN 978-1118301326.</ref><ref>Marinacci, Joshua (2012), Building Mobile Applications with Java p.55-6, O'Reilly Media, ISBN 978-1449308230.</ref>比较知名的智能手机的平台游戏类型为《[[地狱边境|地狱边境]]》(2010年)、《{{link-en|Leo's Fortune|Leo's Fortune}}》(2014年) 等等。

*'''微型卡式录像带'''：在1990年代末以存储卡作为储存媒介的摄像机出现以前当代的摄像机的储存媒介为卡式录像带。日本JVC公司在1983年开发摄像机专用的VHS格式的微型卡式录像带，为当时全世界最轻、最小的卡式录像带VHS Compact，简称VHS-C。随后作为与JVC公司在摄像机市场上的竞争对手的索尼公司便在1984年8月推出了8毫米微型卡式录像带Video8，简称V8，相对于VHS格式来说没有什么区别，但是体积却缩小了。1985年1月索尼还推出了采用V8格式的两款摄像机，CCD-V8和第一款[[Handycam|Handycam]]系列的摄像机CCD-M8。由于摄像机市场上正在进行着VHS Compact与Video8的竞争。因此JVC公司在1987年推出了Super VHS Compact，简称S-VHS-C，即VHS Compact的高带型，它将图象的清晰度将250条扫描线提高到400，尺寸与VHS Compact微型卡式录像带完全相同，Super VHS Compact可以向下兼容VHS Compact录像带。随后索尼公司在1989年公布了Hi-Band V8微型卡式录像带，简称Hi8，也就是V8的高带型。将8毫米的图象质量也从270条扫描线提高到400。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.timelessdvd.com/transfer-video/transfer-hi8.html |title=Hi8, Video 8, Conversion or Transfer to DVD |access-date=2013-07-17 |archive-date=2013-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130529200143/http://www.timelessdvd.com/transfer-video/transfer-hi8.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://columbiaisa.50webs.com/camcord_formats.htm |title=Camcorder formats MiniDV DVD HDD HDV D8 VHS-C |access-date=2013-07-17 |archive-date=2020-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200217172842/http://columbiaisa.50webs.com/camcord_formats.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1986-12-12/entertainment/8604030100_1_zoom-electronic-viewfinder-camcorder |title=Neither Too Big Nor Too Small, Sony`s Auto Handycam Seems Just |access-date=2013-07-19 |archive-date=2017-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924093135/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1986-12-12/entertainment/8604030100_1_zoom-electronic-viewfinder-camcorder |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*'''[[摄像机|摄像机]]'''：1970年代下半叶，[[RCA|RCA]]公司、Ampex公司、池上公司和[[日立製作所|日立]]分别推出世界上第一批可携带的广播摄像机TK-76、BCC-4、HL-77和SK-80，但都不是单体式摄像机，使用时一般必须经一条电缆连接至一台笨重的[[录影机|录影机]]才可以录制影片，例如以索尼U-matic卡式录像带作为储存媒介的VO-3800。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.tvnewscheck.com/playout/tag/tk-76/ |title=ENG in the 1970s: A Personal Look Back |access-date=2017-04-09 |archive-date=2018-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180114232644/http://www.tvnewscheck.com/playout/tag/tk-76/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Abramson, Albert (2003), The History of Television, 1942 to 2000 pp.167, ISBN 0786412208.</ref>日本JVC公司和索尼公司于1983年分别发布了世界上第一批两款家用摄像机BMC-100和GZ-S3U，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.timelessdvd.com/tape-to-dvd/tape-to-dvd.html |title=Tape to DVD: A Brief History |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140329123103/http://www.timelessdvd.com/tape-to-dvd/tape-to-dvd.html |archive-date=2014-03-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.uie.com/articles/more_with_less/ |title=The Evolution of Camera Features |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130804100601/http://www.uie.com/articles/more_with_less/ |archive-date=2013-08-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>Dhir, Amit (2004), The Digital Consumer Technology Handbook: A Comprehensive Guide to Devices, Standards, Future Directions, and Programmable Logic Solutions p.263-4, Newnes Press, ISBN 978-0750678155.</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.videomaker.com/videonews/2011/10/11632-history-of-video-now-and-then-a-look-back |title=History of Video Now and Then  |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2013-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130308100928/http://www.videomaker.com/videonews/2011/10/11632-history-of-video-now-and-then-a-look-back |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rewindmuseum.com/vintagecamcorder.htm |title=Museum of early consumer electronics and 1st achievements |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2021-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112091310/https://www.rewindmuseum.com/vintagecamcorder.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>JVC公司的GZ-S3U分体式摄像机，摄像机和录影机可拆组，使用VHS格式的微型卡式录像带VHS Compact，微型卡式录像带尺寸大小与[[卡式录音带|卡式录音带]]差不多；<ref name="totalrewind2007">{{cite web | url = http://www.totalrewind.org/cameras/C_SFP3.htm | title = Separate camera and recorder; First VHS-C camcorder | accessdate = 2007-09-14 | date = 2007-09-14 | archive-date = 2008-10-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081016045848/http://www.totalrewind.org/cameras/C_SFP3.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://pro.jvc.com/prof/attributes/features.jsp?model_id=MDL101400 |title=JVC GZ-S3U |access-date=2017-04-09 |archive-date=2017-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170910083901/http://pro.jvc.com/prof/attributes/features.jsp?model_id=MDL101400 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.copyvhstodvd.com.au/html/identify_your_tapes.htmlVideo Tape dimension]{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>索尼推出的Betamovie BMC-100摄像机则使用Beta格式的卡式录像带，不属于微型卡式录像带，BMC-100不具备播放功能。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.totalrewind.org/cameras/C_BMC1.htm |title=BetaMovie BMC-100 - Total Rewind |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2018-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180925065224/http://www.totalrewind.org/cameras/C_BMC1.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.digicamhistory.com/1980_1983.html |title=1980s - DigiCamHistory |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2017-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170916172053/http://www.digicamhistory.com/1980_1983.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.totalrewind.org/cameras.htm |title=Evolution Cameras become Camcorders |access-date=2013-07-18 |archive-date=2020-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705030428/http://www.totalrewind.org/cameras.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>1984年JVC公司推出世界上第一款单体式摄像机{{link-en|GR-C1|JVC GR-C1}}，采用VHS Compact微型卡式录像带作为储存媒介，虽然和之前的GZ-S3U一样具备播放功能，不过是单体式，这台摄像机在1985年美国电影《[[回到未来|回到未来]]》中出现。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.totalrewind.org/cameras/C_GRC1.htm |title=JVC GR-C1 - Total Rewind |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2020-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200308203204/http://www.totalrewind.org/cameras/C_GRC1.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.digicamhistory.com/1984_1985.html |title=1984_1985 - DigiCamHistory |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2017-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171001083820/http://www.digicamhistory.com/1984_1985.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.smecc.org/jvc_video.htm |title=JVC VIDEO |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2021-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127152104/http://www.smecc.org/jvc_video.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*'''[[闪存|闪存]]'''：无论是NOR型或NAND型闪存都是[[舛冈富士雄|舛冈富士雄]]在1981年东芝公司工作时发明的，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.usitc.gov/publications/332/journals/rise_flash_memory_market.pdf |title=The Rise of the Flash Memory Market: Its Impact on Firm Behavior and Global Semiconductor Trade Patterns |access-date=2013-07-18 |archive-date=2019-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190111085429/https://www.usitc.gov/publications/332/journals/rise_flash_memory_market.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Fulford|first=Benjamin|title=Unsung hero|work=Forbes|date=24 June 2002|accessdate=18 March 2008|url=http://www.forbes.com/global/2002/0624/030.html|archive-date=2018-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181028013343/https://www.forbes.com/global/2002/0624/030.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>并于1984年的加州旧金山[[電機電子工程師學會|IEEE]]国际电子组件会议 (International Electron Devices Meeting，简称IEDM) 上发表了这项发明。闪存储器是一种[[電子抹除式可複寫唯讀記憶體|電子抹除式可複寫唯讀記憶體]]的形式，允许在操作中被多次擦或写的存储器。这种科术主要用于一般性数据存储，以及在电脑与其他数字产品间交换传输数据，例如[[存储卡|存储卡]]与[[闪存盘|USB盘]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.radio-electronics.com/info/data/semicond/memory/what-is-flash-memory-basics-tutorial.php |title=What is Flash Memory? |access-date=2013-07-18 |archive-date=2018-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180818023613/https://www.radio-electronics.com/info/data/semicond/memory/what-is-flash-memory-basics-tutorial.php |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://computer.howstuffworks.com/flash-memory.htm |title=How Flash Memory Works |access-date=2013-07-18 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126144428/https://computer.howstuffworks.com/flash-memory.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

====下半叶====
*'''[[PC卡|JEIDA存储卡]]'''： 1985年日本电子工业发展协会 (Japan Electronics Industry Development Association，简称JEIDA) 开始研制存储卡。1988年美国个人电脑机内存卡国际协会 (Personal Computer Memory Card International Association，简称PCMCIA) 成立。JEIDA的一些设计思想被美国的PCMCIA (个人电脑机内存卡国际协会) 采纳，例如将68针存储卡接口标准引入到自己的存储卡上，1990年PCMCIA推出1.0版本存储卡，而JEIDA也推出4.0版本存储卡，目的是为了取代现有的软盘软驱。这两个组织都一直致力于推动现在称为[[PC卡|PC卡]]的国际标准，两个版本于1992年11月合并，并发布了该标准最新的版本PCMCIA2.0，亦称JEIDA4.1，成为了首批投入商业生产的[[存储卡|存储卡]]格式。<ref>Park, John (2003). Practical Data Acquisition for Instrumentation and Control Systems p.293. Newnes. ISBN 978-0750657969.</ref><ref>Anderson, Don (1995). PCMCIA System Architecture: 16-Bit PC Cards p.14-5. Addison-Wesley Professional. ISBN 978-0201409918.</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.wisegeek.com/what-is-a-pcmcia-card.htm |title=What Is a PCMCIA Card? |access-date=2013-07-18 |archive-date=2020-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806222027/https://www.wisegeek.com/what-is-a-pcmcia-card.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*'''爽安康氧气健康器'''：世界上第一台爽安康氧气健康器由日本Skylite Industry公司于1988年推出。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.chimachine4u.com/skylite.html |title=Certificate of Approval from Japan for the manufacture ofthe Original Sun Ancon Chi Machine TM by Skylite Corporation,distributed exclusively by Hsin Ten Enterprise - 1990 |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2019-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190607101110/http://www.chimachine4u.com/skylite.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.chimachinestory.org/early-history |title=Chi Machine Story |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130825081619/http://chimachinestory.org/early-history |archive-date=2013-08-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

*'''[[数码相机|卡片数码相机、存储卡数码相机]]'''：[[富士胶片|富士]]公司于1988年10月5日在[[德国|德国]][[科隆|科隆]][[世界影像博览会|世界影像博览会]]展示了世界第一款数码相机、世界第一款卡片数码相机DS-1P。DS-1P是广泛承认的世界上第一款真正的数码相机，也是数码相机史上的重要里程碑，<ref name="Brookes">{{Cite web |url=http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/5-digital-cameras/ |title=5 Things You Didn’t Know About The First Digital Cameras |access-date=2013-07-24 |archive-date=2017-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171205214418/http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/5-digital-cameras/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://camera-wiki.org/wiki/Fujix_DS-1P |title=Fujix DS-1P |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2020-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200127224609/http://camera-wiki.org/wiki/Fujix_DS-1P |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.photographywebsite.co.uk/history-of-the-digital-camera-c643.html |title=History of the Digital Camera |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2020-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803142440/http://www.photographywebsite.co.uk/history-of-the-digital-camera-c643.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.film2usb.com/history-of-photography.html |title=History of Photography - A Hundred-Year Legacy |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304115640/http://www.film2usb.com/history-of-photography.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.practicalphotographytips.com/history-of-digital-photography.html#axzz2ZfFRRrVc |title=History of Digital Photography |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120819035249/http://www.practicalphotographytips.com/history-of-digital-photography.html#axzz2ZfFRRrVc |archive-date=2012-08-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://wanttoknowit.com/when-was-the-digital-camera-invented/ |title=When Was the Digital Camera Invented |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128113910/https://wanttoknowit.com/when-was-the-digital-camera-invented/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.whenwasitinvented.org/when-was-the-digital-camera-invented/ |title=When was the Digital Camera invented? |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2017-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171029091520/http://www.whenwasitinvented.org/when-was-the-digital-camera-invented/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://photography.lovetoknow.com/Who_Invented_the_Digital_Camera |title=Who Invented the Digital Camera |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024034427/https://photography.lovetoknow.com/Who_Invented_the_Digital_Camera |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="digicammuseum">{{Cite web |url=http://www.digicammuseum.com/en/history |title=History of the digital camera and digital imaging |access-date=2017-09-24 |archive-date=2015-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150527104605/http://www.digicammuseum.com/en/history |dead-url=yes }}</ref>首次搭载了东芝开发的SRAM存储卡，容量为16MB，是第一款完全数字化的文件格式相机，也是以存储卡作为储存媒介的数码相机的最早原型。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.digicamhistory.com/1988.html |title=1988 - DigiCamHistory |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2020-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729221426/http://www.digicamhistory.com/1988.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://photography.lovetoknow.com/When_Was_the_First_Digital_Camera_Made |title=When Was the First Digital Camera Made |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2020-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808230607/https://photography.lovetoknow.com/When_Was_the_First_Digital_Camera_Made |dead-url=no }}</ref>该相机没有上市，但富士于1989年推出了全球第一款以存储卡作为储存媒介的商业化数码相机DS-X。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://petapixel.com/2016/06/09/photo-history-worlds-first-fully-digital-camera-invented-fuji/ |title=The World's First 'Fully' Digital Camera was Created by Fuji - PetaPixel |access-date=2017-09-24 |archive-date=2020-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028132215/https://petapixel.com/2016/06/09/photo-history-worlds-first-fully-digital-camera-invented-fuji/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>东芝分别于1990年和1993年推出以存储卡作为储存媒介的数码单反相机MC200和升级版MC200A；柯达从1994年8月开始柯达便在{{link-en|DCS 400系列|Kodak DCS 400 series}}数码单反相机搭载了[[PC卡|PCMCIA]]三型介面存储卡作为储存媒介，最高可支持340MB容量，从此舍弃巨大无比的外置硬盘。<ref>digicamhistory [http://www.digicamhistory.com/1990.html 1990] {{Wayback|url=http://www.digicamhistory.com/1990.html |date=20100626090027 }}, [http://www.digicamhistory.com/1993.html 1993] {{Wayback|url=http://www.digicamhistory.com/1993.html |date=20200926145532 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://apphotnum.free.fr/N2BE10.html |title=Kodak DCS cameras based on Nikon |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2009-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090426081740/http://apphotnum.free.fr/N2BE10.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mir.com.my/rb/photography/companies/Kodak/index1.htm |title=A brief info on Kodak DCS-Series Digital Still SLR cameras Part II - DCS-400 Series with Nikon N90(s)/F90(x) body Chassis |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024093753/https://www.mir.com.my/rb/photography/companies/Kodak/index1.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>随着[[数码摄影|数码摄影]]的首次出现，也逐渐取代了[[胶片|胶片]]摄影；2006年1月12日，日本[[尼康|尼康]]宣布，将停止其传统胶片相机生产。同年5月25日，佳能召开记者发布会，明确了今后不研发胶片相机新产品的方针。<ref>[http://www.dpreview.com/news/2006/1/12/nikon_news Nikon to focus on digital]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.forbes.com/2006/05/25/canon-camera-uchida-cx_po_0525autofacescan07.html |title=Uchida Says Canon To Stop Developing Film Cameras |access-date=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2013-07-21 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130721035445/http://www.forbes.com/2006/05/25/canon-camera-uchida-cx_po_0525autofacescan07.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>美国[[柯达|柯达]]公司工程师史蒂文·赛尚曾设计出一部黑白图像的数码相机，将影像储存在[[卡式录音带|卡式录音带]]中，和胶片一样使用塑胶薄膜，不过这款相机相当笨重，且没有销售，在数据存储方面都还没有做到文件格式系统。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://petapixel.com/2010/08/05/the-worlds-first-digital-camera-by-kodak-and-steve-sasson/ |title=The World’s First Digital Camera by Kodak and Steve Sasson |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2020-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201223020900/https://petapixel.com/2010/08/05/the-worlds-first-digital-camera-by-kodak-and-steve-sasson/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.freedoniagroup.com/pdf/2086smwe.pdf |title=Plastic Film |access-date=2013-07-24 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304121342/http://www.freedoniagroup.com/pdf/2086smwe.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*'''数码卡式录像带、数码摄像机'''：索尼于1986年推出世界上第一款[[数字视频|数码卡式录像带]]{{link-en|D-1|D-1 (Sony)}}，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thegreatbear.net/video-tape/d1-d2-d3-histories-digital-video-tape/ |title=D1, D2 & D3 – histories of digital video tape |access-date=2016-05-24 |archive-date=2020-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201226071621/https://thegreatbear.net/video-tape/d1-d2-d3-histories-digital-video-tape/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>1995年7月索尼推出两款专业摄像机DCR-VX1000和DCR-VX700，第一次采用[[DV|Digital Video]]数码格式的微型卡式录像带，开创了摄像机的数码时代。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dvinfo.net/pages/dv_formt.htm |title=Consumer and Professional Digital Video (DV) |access-date=2016-05-24 |archive-date=2017-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112040728/http://www.dvinfo.net/pages/dv_formt.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.videomaker.com/article/c5/2381-digital-video-now-available-to-consumers |title=DIGITAL VIDEO NOW AVAILABLE TO CONSUMERS |access-date=2016-05-24 |archive-date=2020-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200523105946/https://www.videomaker.com/article/c5/2381-digital-video-now-available-to-consumers |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.digital-mp3-world.com/learn-the-development-story-of-digital-video-camcorders |title=Learn The Development Story Of Digital Video Camcorders |access-date=2016-05-24 |archive-date=2016-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603192749/http://www.digital-mp3-world.com/learn-the-development-story-of-digital-video-camcorders |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*'''[[多人在线战斗竞技场游戏|MOBA游戏类型]]'''：以美国[[Riot_Games|Riot Games]]公司于2009年10月27日推出的《[[英雄联盟|英雄联盟]]》为例子，多人在线战斗竞技场游戏类型是目前营收最高的游戏类型。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ibtimes.com/game-revenue-could-reach-115b-2020-moba-mobile-titles-leading-way-2280900 |title=Game Revenue Could Reach B By 2020, With MOBA And Mobile Titles Leading The Way |access-date=2017-10-07 |archive-date=2020-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200616235834/https://www.ibtimes.com/game-revenue-could-reach-115b-2020-moba-mobile-titles-leading-way-2280900 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2015-03-30-mobas-will-overtake-mmorpgs-in-f2p-revenue-this-year-eedar |title=MOBAs will overtake MMORPGs in F2P revenue this year - EEDAR {{!}} GamesIndustry.biz |access-date=2017-10-07 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108134951/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2015-03-30-mobas-will-overtake-mmorpgs-in-f2p-revenue-this-year-eedar |dead-url=no }}</ref>MOBA或多人在线战斗竞技场游戏类型，[[即时战略游戏|即时战略游戏]] (RTS) 发展史上的衍生版。即时战略游戏最早于1981年出现，该词最早出现于1982年12月刊登的美国杂志《{{link-en|BYTE|Byte (magazine)}}》，但最早被游戏设计师{{link-en|布瑞特·斯帕里|Brett Sperry}}于1992年定名。<ref name=a>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/gamespot/features/all/real_time/|title=A History of Real-Time Strategy Games|accessdate=March 31, 2008|author=Bruce Geryk|publisher=GameSpot|archive-date=2011-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110427052656/http://gamespot.com/gamespot/features/all/real_time/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=b>{{cite web|url=http://archive.gamespy.com/top10/february04/rts|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100616031405/http://archive.gamespy.com/top10/february04/rts|archivedate=2010-06-16|title=Top ten real-time strategy games of all time|publisher=GameSpy|accessdate=December 2, 2008|dead-url=no}}</ref>一般被认为最早的即时战略游戏为美国{{link-en|Evryware|Evryware}}公司于1984年推出的《{{link-en|上古战争艺术|The Ancient Art of War}}》；<ref name=1UP-Duke>{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/do/feature?cId=3134179|title=Hail to the Duke|author=Scott Sharkey|publisher=1UP.com|accessdate=March 1, 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20040913063641/http://www.1up.com/do/feature?cId=3134179|archivedate=2004年9月13日}}</ref>日本{{link-en|Technosoft|Technosoft}}公司于1989年12月15日在[[Mega_Drive|Sega Genesis]]游戏主机上推出的《{{link-en|离子战机|Herzog Zwei}}》是一款一人一半屏幕的[[双打|对战]]即时战略游戏，需要双方各控制一架变身机器人的飞机，不断的建造士兵、坦克等，以推翻对方的基地为目标，这款游戏不仅被认为是最早的真正意义上现代即时战略游戏或RTS，<ref name=hzweifirstrts>{{cite web | url=http://gamespy-archives.quaddicted.com/sites/www.strategyplanet.com/features/articles/strategypeak/index.html | title=Are Real Time Strategy Games At Their Peak? | publisher=[[GameSpy|GameSpy]] | date=May 9, 2001 | accessdate=December 14, 2014 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729043300/https://gamespy-archives.quaddicted.com/sites/www.strategyplanet.com/features/articles/strategypeak/index.html | archive-date=2017-07-29 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=zzap>Zzap! Issue 68, December 1990, p.45 – {{cite web | url=http://www.classicgaming.com/amigareviews/battlema.htm | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060211022753/http://www.classicgaming.com/amigareviews/battlema.htm | archivedate=2006-02-11 | title=Amiga Reviews: Battlemaster | accessdate=December 17, 2006 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="TechRadar2006RTSGaming">{{Cite web |url=http://www.techradar.com/news/gaming/the-past-present-and-future-of-rts-gaming-634983?src=rss&attr=newsgaming |title=The past, present and future of RTS gaming – TechRadar UK |last=Cobbett |first=R. |date=27 September 2006 |publisher=Future Publishing Limited |accessdate=23 November 2009 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090928061215/http://www.techradar.com/news/gaming/the-past-present-and-future-of-rts-gaming-634983?src=rss&attr=newsgaming |archivedate=2009-09-28 }}</ref>也被认为是多人在线战斗竞技场游戏或MOBA的始祖。<ref name="mcvuk">Greg Lockley (3 June 2014), [http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/moba-the-story-so-far/0133335 MOBA: The story so far] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/moba-the-story-so-far/0133335 |date=20170427151821 }}, [[Market_for_Home_Computing_and_Video_Games|Market for Home Computing and Video Games]]</ref><ref name="gamesradar">Andrew Groen (7 March 2012), [http://www.gamesradar.com/ask-gr-anything-whats-moba/ Ask GR Anything: What's a MOBA?] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gamesradar.com/ask-gr-anything-whats-moba/ |date=20170630043636 }}, [[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2017/09/build-gather-brawl-repeat-the-history-of-real-time-strategy-games/2/ |title=Build, gather, brawl, repeat: The history of real-time strategy games {{!}} Ars Technica |access-date=2017-10-07 |archive-date=2017-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171004034519/https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2017/09/build-gather-brawl-repeat-the-history-of-real-time-strategy-games/2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>该游戏部分影响了后来美国[[西木工作室|西木工作室]]于1992年推出的《[[沙丘II_新王朝|沙丘魔堡2]]》，<ref name="origin_rts">{{cite web|last=Clarke-Willson|first=Stephen|title=The Origin of Realtime Strategy Games on the PC|url=http://www.above-the-garage.com/blog/1998/8/18/the-origin-of-realtime-strategy-games-on-the-pc|work=The Rise and Fall of Virgin Interactive|publisher=Above the Garage Productions|accessdate=30 January 2012|authorlink=Stephen Clarke-Willson|date=August 18, 1998|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20030504034920/http://www.above-the-garage.com/rblts/vie16b.htm|archivedate=2003-05-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Edge 2008">{{cite web|title=The Making of... Dune II|url=http://www.edge-online.com/features/the-making-of-dune-ii/|work=''[[Edge_(magazine)|Edge]]''|publisher=Next-Gen.biz|accessdate=July 27, 2011|date=December 9, 2008|archive-date=2015-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150127100120/http://www.edge-online.com/features/the-making-of-dune-ii/|dead-url=no}}</ref>其后《沙丘魔堡2》还影响了[[暴雪娱乐|暴雪娱乐]]公司于1994年推出的《[[魔兽争霸：人类与兽人|魔兽争霸]]》。<ref name = ignstate>{{cite web |last=Adams |first=Dan |title=The State of the RTS |publisher=IGN |date=April 7, 2006 |url=http://pc.ign.com/articles/700/700747p1.html |accessdate=May 31, 2007 |archive-date=2008-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080511142804/http://pc.ign.com/articles/700/700747p1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=codeofhonor>{{Cite web |url=https://www.codeofhonor.com/blog/the-making-of-warcraft-part-1 |title=The making of Warcraft part 1 - Code Of Honor |access-date=2017-10-07 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112041808/https://www.codeofhonor.com/blog/the-making-of-warcraft-part-1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>美国Carbon Games公司于2012年10月5日推出的《{{link-en|空甲联盟|AirMech}}》是献给《离子战机》的升级版制作，游戏还加入了现代多人互联网对战。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://levelskip.com/action-adventure/AirMech-Strike-Split |title=AirMech Strike: A PvP-Oriented Relaunch of a Struggling Herzog Zwei Tribute |access-date=2017-10-07 |archive-date=2017-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171003175716/https://levelskip.com/action-adventure/AirMech-Strike-Split |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-05-26-herzog-zwei-retrospective |title=Herzog Zwei retrospective |access-date=2017-10-07 |archive-date=2019-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129195632/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-05-26-herzog-zwei-retrospective |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*'''[[游戏机|光盘主机]]'''：美国[[快捷半導體公司|快捷半導體公司]]于1976年11月1日推出世界上第一个以[[ROM卡带|ROM卡带]]作为储存媒介的主机[[Fairchild_Channel_F|Fairchild Channel F]]。1979年随着CD的出现[[NEC|NEC]]与[[Hudson_Soft|Hudson Soft]]在1987年10月30日于日本推出世界上第一台支持以光盘作为储存媒介的主机[[PC_Engine|PC Engine]]，这台游戏机在1989年8月29日于北美出售，在北美称作TurboGrafx-16 Entertainment SuperSystem，简称TG-16。PC Engine最初使用的是一种名为HuCard的[[集成电路|IC卡型]]卡带，后来NEC在1988年4月12日于日本推出了外接CD-ROM扩充设备PC-Engine CD-ROM²和与主机连接的Interface Unit连接单元，改为使用光盘作为游戏的存储介质，是世界上第一台采用光盘媒体的家用游戏机，这台外接扩充设备在1990年8月1日于北美以TurboGrafx-CD的名称发售，拥有大量的光盘游戏支援，不过大部分仅限于日本销售而非北美。<ref name="NEC TurboGrafx 16 CD Game Console">{{Cite web |url=http://www.thegameconsole.com/nec-turbo-grafx-16-cd/ |title=NEC TurboGrafx 16 CD Game Console |access-date=2017-09-27 |archive-date=2020-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200103004636/http://www.thegameconsole.com/nec-turbo-grafx-16-cd/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NEC TurboGrafx 16 CD Game Console"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://classicgaming.gamespy.com/View.php?view=ConsoleMuseum.Detail&id=32&game=15 |title=NEC TurboGrafx-16 (TG16) - 1989-1993 - Classic Gaming |access-date=2013-07-26 |archive-date=2011-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721063421/http://classicgaming.gamespy.com/View.php?view=ConsoleMuseum.Detail&id=32&game=15 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.videogameconsolelibrary.com/pg80-pc_eng_cd.htm#page=reviews |title=NEC PC Engine CD-ROM2 \ TurboGrafx-CD |access-date=2017-09-27 |archive-date=2020-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026232408/http://www.videogameconsolelibrary.com/pg80-pc_eng_cd.htm#page=reviews |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.supergaijinultragamer.org/2012/03/nec-pc-engine-interface-unit-the-suitcase-bomb/ |title=NEC PC Engine CD-ROM2 Interface Unit – The Suitcase Bomb |access-date=2017-09-27 |archive-date=2020-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921134210/https://www.supergaijinultragamer.org/2012/03/nec-pc-engine-interface-unit-the-suitcase-bomb/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>1991年9月21日NEC推出将主机和外接CD-ROM扩充设备一体化的游戏机{{link-en|PC Engine Duo|TurboDuo}}，在北美市场于1992年10月10日以TurboDuo的名称发售，成为第一台内置CD-ROM光驱的游戏机，随后富士通也在1993年2月20日于日本推出内置CD-ROM光驱的游戏机[[FM_Towns_Marty|FM Towns Marty]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://thngs.co/things/6634 |title=Turbo Duo |access-date=2017-09-27 |archive-date=2019-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190123200935/https://thngs.co/things/6634 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gamepilgrimage.com/book/export/html/10923 |title=Turbo DUO |access-date=2013-07-26 |archive-date=2016-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827101403/http://gamepilgrimage.com/book/export/html/10923 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.videogameconsolelibrary.com/pg90-fm_towns.htm#page=reviews |title=FM Towns Marty |access-date=2013-07-26 |archive-date=2019-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815173149/http://www.videogameconsolelibrary.com/pg90-fm_towns.htm#page=reviews |dead-url=no }}</ref>索尼公司于1991年6月2日在[[芝加哥|芝加哥]][[消费电子展|消费电子展]]览会上展示了名为Play Station的游戏主机，可支持超级任天堂{{link-en|外接光盘扩充设备|Super NES CD-ROM}} (SFC-CD)上的索尼Super Disc也可以支持其卡带游戏，该主机为白色其外观类似超级任天堂，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/1991/06/03/business/nintendo-philips-deal-is-a-slap-at-sony.html |title=Nintendo-Philips Deal Is a Slap at Sony |access-date=2017-09-27 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111223531/https://www.nytimes.com/1991/06/03/business/nintendo-philips-deal-is-a-slap-at-sony.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/1998/08/28/history-of-the-playstation |title=HISTORY OF THE PLAYSTATION |access-date=2017-09-27 |archive-date=2012-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120218120358/http://psx.ign.com/articles/060/060188p1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.altpress.com/news/entry/this_old_playstation_console_was_built_by_nintendo_and_sony |title=This old PlayStation console was built by Nintendo and Sony |access-date=2017-09-27 |archive-date=2017-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170928010224/http://www.altpress.com/news/entry/this_old_playstation_console_was_built_by_nintendo_and_sony |dead-url=no }}</ref>其后又在1994年12月3日推出[[PlayStation|PlayStation]]光盘游戏主机，PlayStation虽并非第一台光盘游戏主机，但它的问世却改变了此后游戏主机发展的方向。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.themill.com/millchannel/244/20-years-of-play-a-look-back-at-iconic-playstation-ads |title=20 Years of Play: A Look Back at Iconic PlayStation Ads |access-date=2017-09-27 |archive-date=2019-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191021195014/http://www.themill.com/millchannel/244/20-years-of-play-a-look-back-at-iconic-playstation-ads |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.racketboy.com/retro/sony/ps1/sony-playstation-ps1-101-a-beginners-guide |title=SONY PLAYSTATION (PS1) 101: A BEGINNERS GUIDE |access-date=2017-09-27 |archive-date=2017-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171122230532/http://www.racketboy.com/retro/sony/ps1/sony-playstation-ps1-101-a-beginners-guide |dead-url=no }}</ref>可以说PC Engine和Playstation的出现决定了此后的[[电子游戏机|第四代到第八代]]游戏机各种不同光盘，例如[[PlayStation|PlayStation]]、[[Sega_Saturn|Sega Saturn]]、[[PlayStation_2|PlayStation 2]] 、[[Dreamcast|Dreamcast]]、[[任天堂GameCube|GameCube]]、[[Wii|Wii]]、[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]、[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]成为主力游戏媒体的发展方向，从此取代了[[ROM卡带|ROM卡带]]游戏机；这些游戏主机虽使用不同光盘格式，例如CD-ROM、DVD、[[GD-ROM|GD-ROM]]、[[任天堂光盘|GameCube Game Disc]]、HD DVD和[[蓝光光盘|蓝光光盘]]，但都属于光盘游戏主机，以光盘作为作为储存媒介。

*'''[[液晶显示器|液晶电视]]'''：日本[[卡西歐|卡西歐]]公司于1983年6月推出了2.7英寸黑白液晶显示屏的携带式电视TV-10，这是世界上第一款液晶显示屏电视。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thisisthefirst.com/visual/35-the-first-%E6%B6%B2%E6%99%B6-television |title=The First 液晶 Television |access-date=2021-06-26 |archive-date=2019-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190123200935/http://www.thisisthefirst.com/visual/35-the-first-%E6%B6%B2%E6%99%B6-television |dead-url=no }}</ref>1988年6月24日[[夏普|夏普]]公司成功研制出14英寸彩色TFT液晶显示器，这顶技术的成功彻底改变了在此之后的家用电视、电脑[[显示器|显示器]]。<ref name="HIROHISA KAWAMOTO">{{Cite web |url=http://www.lcd-displays-manufacturers.com/suserfiles/upload/lcd_history_blaze_display.pdf |title=The History of Liquid-Crystal Displays |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2013-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130121144533/http://www.lcd-displays-manufacturers.com/suserfiles/upload/lcd_history_blaze_display.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sharp-world.com/corporate/info/his/only_one/item/t22.html |title=World's First 14-Inch Color TFT LCD |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2019-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190923232942/http://www.sharp-world.com/corporate/info/his/only_one/item/t22.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*'''[[平板显示器|平板电视、平板电脑显示器]]'''：1988年6月24日[[夏普|夏普]]公司成功研制出14英寸彩色TFT液晶显示器，为平板显示器史上的重要里程碑，在此之前的所谓液晶屏幕显示器甚至平板显示器都仅采用在[[手表|电子手表]]、[[计算器|袖珍计算器]]、当代黑白屏[[笔记本|电脑笔记本]]和其他携带产品的小屏幕上，而作为家用电视、台式电脑显示器，包括现代电脑笔记本，最低屏幕需求为14英寸，因此1988年可以说是[[平板显示器|平板显示器]]取代家用传统[[CRT|CRT]]显示屏的年代之始。<ref name="HIROHISA KAWAMOTO"/>1996年9月，夏普公司在[[消费电子展|消费电子展]]展示40英寸1280x768彩色TFT液晶显示器，由2块29英寸液晶屏拼接而成。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sharp-world.com/corporate/info/his/h_company/1996/index.html |title=Sharp History |access-date=2017-09-24 |archive-date=2019-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190920133918/http://www.sharp-world.com/corporate/info/his/h_company/1996/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Castellano, Joseph A. (2005), Liquid Gold: The Story Of Liquid Crystal Displays and the Creation of an Industry p.284-5, World Scientific Publishing Company, ISBN 978-9812389565.</ref>最早一批采用彩色TFT液晶显示屏的电脑笔记本包括1992年4月27日推出的9英寸{{link-en|日本电气 UltraLite|NEC UltraLite}} SL/25C、1992年10月5日推出的10.5英寸[[IBM|IBM]] [[ThinkPad|ThinkPad]] 700C等等。<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=5D0EAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA11&lpg=PA11&dq=nec+sl/25c++1992&source=bl&ots=HY9dN1fKc3&sig=7gVvJ95_Sy6w2Ywzmsvmg8E9TVY&hl=en&sa=X&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=nec%20sl%2F25c%20%201992&f=false InfoWorld - 27 Apr 1992]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://online.wsj.com/adimg/sas-laptop-history.pdf |title=A look at laptop history |access-date=2017-09-24 |archive-date=2019-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191024004446/http://online.wsj.com/adimg/sas-laptop-history.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.zdnet.com/article/happy-20th-birthday-to-the-ibm-thinkpad-a-design-classic/ |title=Happy 20th birthday to the IBM ThinkPad: a design classic |access-date=2017-09-24 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108114110/http://www.zdnet.com/article/happy-20th-birthday-to-the-ibm-thinkpad-a-design-classic/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://oldcomputers.net/ibm-thinkpad.html |title=IBM ThinkPad notebook |access-date=2017-09-24 |archive-date=2021-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127080733/http://oldcomputers.net/ibm-thinkpad.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>日本[[藝卓|藝卓]]公司在1992年推出10.4英寸彩色TFT液晶[[显示器|电脑显示器]]FA-1020，为最早的台式电脑平板显示器之一，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.eizoglobal.com/company/information/history/ |title=Company History |access-date=2017-09-24 |archive-date=2021-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120100246/https://www.eizoglobal.com/company/information/history/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>1990年代台式电脑平板显示器品牌还包括[[優派|優派]]、IBM和苹果公司，例如苹果于1998年推出的15英寸[[Apple_Studio_Display|Apple Studio Display]]台式电脑显示器，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.pcworld.com/article/209224/displays/historic-monitors-slideshow.html#slide19 |title=A Brief History of Computer Displays |access-date=2017-09-24 |archive-date=2019-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190222023019/https://www.pcworld.com/article/209224/displays/historic-monitors-slideshow.html#slide19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2003年台式电脑液晶显示器或平板电脑显示器在全球销售量上首次超过台式电脑CRT显示器，在台式电脑显示器上占主导份额。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.itworld.com/article/2805952/hardware/idc--%E6%B6%B2%E6%99%B6s-to-outsell-crt-monitors-in-2003.html |title=IDC: 液晶s to outsell CRT monitors in 2003 |access-date=2021-06-26 |archive-date=2019-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190123200935/https://www.itworld.com/article/2805952/hardware/idc--%E6%B6%B2%E6%99%B6s-to-outsell-crt-monitors-in-2003.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>而平板电视机在全球销售量上也于2007年首次超过传统CRT电视机。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.theregister.co.uk/2008/02/22/displaysearch_crt_lcd_global_q4/ |title=Global LCD TV sales overtake CRT |access-date=2017-09-24 |archive-date=2018-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180703050802/https://www.theregister.co.uk/2008/02/22/displaysearch_crt_lcd_global_q4/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.afterdawn.com/news/article.cfm/2008/02/21/lcd_sales_surpass_crt_during_last_part_of_2007 |title=LCD sales surpass CRT during last part of 2007 |access-date=2017-09-24 |archive-date=2017-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924095519/http://www.afterdawn.com/news/article.cfm/2008/02/21/lcd_sales_surpass_crt_during_last_part_of_2007 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

