*'''[[碳纳米管|碳纳米管]]'''：碳纳米管是在1991年1月由日本筑波NEC实验室的物理学家[[饭岛澄男|饭岛澄男]]使用高分辨率分析电镜从电弧法生产的[[碳纤维|碳纤维]]中发现的<ref>{{lang|en|S.Iijima, ''[[Nature|Nature]]'', '''354'''(1991),56.}}</ref>。它是一种管状的碳分子，管上每个碳原子采取[[sp2杂化|sp<sup>2</sup>杂化]]，相互之间以碳-碳[[σ键|σ键]]结合起来，形成由六边形组成的蜂窝状结构作为碳纳米管的骨架。

*'''[[游戏机|主机存储卡、主机游戏存档]]'''：最早可存档的游戏为[[电脑游戏|电脑游戏]]，例如在[[柏拉图系统|PALTO]]系统上的第一个电脑迷宫探索游戏《[[pedit5|pedit5]]》(1975年) 和[[个人电脑|个人电脑]]上使用软盘存档的1982年3月推出的[[IBM_PC|IBM PC]]平台版[[电子角色扮演游戏|角色扮演游戏]]《{{link-en|Temple of Apshai|Temple of Apshai}}》(1979年) 等等。<ref name="foulger198212">{{cite journal | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=vy3cBZkjbZgC&lpg=PP1&pg=RA1-PA150#v=onepage&q&f=true | title=From Stock Portfolios to Art Portfolios | work=PC: The Independent Guide to Personal Computers | volume=1 | issue=7 | date=November 1982 | accessdate=21 October 2013 | author=Foulger, David | pages=150–164 | archive-date=2014-01-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140131195653/http://books.google.com/books?id=vy3cBZkjbZgC&lpg=PP1&pg=RA1-PA150#v=onepage&q&f=true | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="cgw_198204">{{Cite journal|work=[[Computer_Gaming_World|Computer Gaming World]]|date=March–April 1982|volume=2|url=http://www.cgwmuseum.org/galleries/index.php?year=1982&pub=2&id=3|issue=2|page=2|title=Hobby and Industry News|journal=|access-date=2017-10-02|archive-date=2020-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026063619/http://www.cgwmuseum.org/galleries/index.php?year=1982&pub=2&id=3|dead-url=no}}</ref>世界上最早可存档的[[街机游戏|街机游戏]]为日本[[太东|太东]]公司于1978年推出的《[[太空侵略者|太空侵略者]]》，它能将高分记录保存，该游戏由[[西角友宏|西角友宏]]设计。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/technology-22714047 |title=Space Invaders: Blast from the past that still inspires |access-date=2017-09-29 |archive-date=2018-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180722131743/https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-22714047 |dead-url=no }}</ref>早期的[[游戏主机|游戏主机]]没有存档功能，因此没有大型长篇的游戏的出现，任天堂公司在日本推出两款外接扩充设备，最早于1984年推出松下制造的{{link-en|FC磁带机|Famicom Data Recorder}}，采用卡式录音带存档，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/feature/27929/nintendos-expansion-ports-famicom-basic-and-data-recorder |title=Famicom BASIC and Data Recorder - Feature - Nintendo World Report |access-date=2017-10-07 |archive-date=2020-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200106013046/http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/feature/27929/nintendos-expansion-ports-famicom-basic-and-data-recorder |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://kotaku.com/nintendos-first-proper-console-was-so-80s-it-had-a-cas-793994070 |title=Nintendo's First Proper Console Was So 80s It Had A Cassette Deck |access-date=2017-10-07 |archive-date=2020-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114190254/https://kotaku.com/nintendos-first-proper-console-was-so-80s-it-had-a-cas-793994070 |dead-url=no }}</ref>其后于1986年推出[[FC磁碟机|FC磁碟机]]，支持软盘存档。<ref name="nintendolife">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2010/11/feature_slipped_disk_the_history_of_the_famicom_disk_system |title=Feature: Slipped Disk - The History of the Famicom Disk System |access-date=2017-10-07 |archive-date=2019-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191219221055/http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2010/11/feature_slipped_disk_the_history_of_the_famicom_disk_system |dead-url=no }}</ref>但在日本以外最早存档方式是保存在[[ROM卡带|ROM卡带]]内的SRAM，采用ROM卡带主板上的一颗[[钮扣电池|钮扣电池]]供电，保证关机后游戏档案也不会丢失。<ref name="nintendolife"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://motherboard.vice.com/en_us/article/pggkmn/pictures-how-to-replace-an-snes-cartridge-save-game-battery |title=How to Replace an SNES Cartridge's Save Game Battery |access-date=2017-09-29 |archive-date=2019-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190506121648/https://motherboard.vice.com/en_us/article/pggkmn/pictures-how-to-replace-an-snes-cartridge-save-game-battery |dead-url=no }}</ref>世界上第一个采用的这类存档方式的是任天堂公司在北美于1987年7月推出的ROM卡带版角色扮演游戏《[[塞尔达传说_(游戏)|塞尔达传说]]》，该游戏由[[宫本茂|宫本茂]]和[[手冢卓志|手冢卓志]]设计。<ref name="nintendolife"/><ref name="NP-20">{{Citation|date=January 1991|title=Why Your Game Paks Never Forget|periodical=[[Nintendo_Power|Nintendo Power]]|publisher=Nintendo|issue=20|pages=28–31}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.howtogeek.com/trivia/what-was-the-first-console-video-game-to-save-a-players-progress/ |title=What Was The First Console Video Game To Save A Player’s Progress? |access-date=2017-09-29 |archive-date=2017-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170929232404/https://www.howtogeek.com/trivia/what-was-the-first-console-video-game-to-save-a-players-progress/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>另一种存档方式是利用游戏提供的[[密码_(电子游戏)|密码]]返回最后游戏的阶段，例如任天堂在北美于1987年8月推出的卡带版《[[银河战士_(游戏)|银河战士]]》。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.n-sider.com/contentview.php?contentid=4180 |title=Mysterious curiosities of the Famicom Disk System |access-date=2017-09-29 |archive-date=2017-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170929231514/http://www.n-sider.com/contentview.php?contentid=4180 |dead-url=no }}</ref>1990年4月26日日本公司[[SNK|SNK]]推出全球最早支持存储卡的游戏主机[[Neo_Geo|Neo Geo]]，其存储卡名为Neo Geo Memory Card。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.neogeoprotos.com/memcardfaq.htm |title=NEO-GEO Memory Card FAQ April 29, 2002 Billy Pitt |access-date=2017-09-29 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108100006/http://www.neogeoprotos.com/memcardfaq.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://retrogamingmagazine.com/magician-lord-brings-adventure-gaming-neo-geo-today-history-april-26th-1990/ |title=MAGICIAN LORD BRINGS ADVENTURE GAMING TO THE NEO GEO: TODAY IN HISTORY- APRIL 26TH, 1990 |access-date=2017-09-29 |archive-date=2017-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170929234023/http://retrogamingmagazine.com/magician-lord-brings-adventure-gaming-neo-geo-today-history-april-26th-1990/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>早期的游戏主机存储卡不是用于扩展空间的，而是用于存档，其后索尼公司在1994年推出的[[PlayStation|PlayStation]]也有该主机专用的存储卡，2001年任天堂推出的[[GameCube|GameCube]]也以存储卡储存存档，2001年后内置硬盘在游戏主机的出现和云同步最终取代了以储存卡存档的方式。

*'''[[手柄|主机手柄的肩上按键]]'''：最早的注入游戏主机手柄的肩上按键为任天堂公司于1990年11月21日推出的[[超级任天堂|超级任天堂]]主机。<ref name="great-controller-firsts">{{Cite web |url=http://arcadesushi.com/great-controller-firsts/ |title=10 Great Controller Firsts |access-date=2017-10-02 |archive-date=2015-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150217035502/http://arcadesushi.com/great-controller-firsts/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*'''摄像机显示屏'''：夏普公司在1992年推出了采用V8及Hi8各式摄像带的ViewCam系列摄像机，这是世界上第一批以显示屏提供实时取景的摄像机、第一批配有液晶显示屏的摄像机。它突破手提摄象机的惯常设计，以彩色液晶显示屏取代传统的取景器。在拍摄过程中，拍摄者可即时在液晶上，观看拍摄到的影象，免除一面单眼窥视取景器，一面操作的困难，令摄象更加容易。此后显示屏成为各大厂牌摄像机的主要配件。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.humansinvent.com/#!/429/sharp-takes-its-name-from-a-mechanical-pencil/ |title=Sharp takes its name from a mechanical pencil |access-date=2013-07-17 |archive-date=2012-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121014123843/http://www.humansinvent.com/#!/429/sharp-takes-its-name-from-a-mechanical-pencil/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.steves-digicams.com/knowledge-center/how-tos/camcorder-operation/how-to-use-the-lcd-screen-on-a-digital-camcorder.html |title=How To Use the LCD Screen on a Digital Camcorder |access-date=2013-07-17 |archive-date=2017-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170909212448/http://www.steves-digicams.com/knowledge-center/how-tos/camcorder-operation/how-to-use-the-lcd-screen-on-a-digital-camcorder.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.businessweek.com/stories/1993-10-31/camcorders-with-the-big-picture Camcorders With The Big Picture]</ref>

*'''[[MiniDisc|MD]]'''：MiniDisc，简称MD。1986年索尼技术人员鹤岛克明研制出可单次写入的光盘 (Write Once Disc，简称WO)，又在1988年研制出可多次擦写的磁光盘 (Magneto Optical Disc，简称MO)。索尼在1989年音响展会 (Audio Fair) 上展示了可擦写的CD原型产品，该产品于1987年被研制出，是索尼与[[KDDI|KDD]] (日本国际电信电话) 共同开发的技术。鹤岛克明开始在MO技术上研制64毫米直径 (面积为光盘的1/4) 可录制74分钟 (和CD一样) 的光盘，并于1991年5月成功，MD由此诞生。MD于1992年9月发布，并在11月的日本，和12月的美国、欧洲出售。<ref name="MD">{{Cite web |url=http://www.sony.net/SonyInfo/CorporateInfo/History/SonyHistory/2-10.html |title=Studio Recorders Go Digital |access-date=2013-07-24 |archive-date=2020-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729225252/https://www.sony.net/SonyInfo/CorporateInfo/History/SonyHistory/2-10.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*'''MD随身听'''：索尼在1992年11月推出MD随身听MZ-1 (录放) 、MZ-2P (单放) 和可单次录制的MD光盘MDW-60，MZ-1售价为750美元。<ref name="MD"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/musicblog/2012/sep/24/sony-minidisc-20-years |title=MiniDisc, the forgotten format |access-date=2013-07-24 |archive-date=2013-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130205215319/http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/musicblog/2012/sep/24/sony-minidisc-20-years |dead-url=no }}</ref>其他厂牌也发布MZ-1的克隆版，例如日本[[AIWA|AIWA]]公司推出的AMD-100和在韩国销售的金星 (LG) MD-R1。<ref>minidisc.org [http://www.minidisc.org/part_Sony_MZ-1.html Sony MZ-1, Goldstar MD-R1] {{Wayback|url=http://www.minidisc.org/part_Sony_MZ-1.html |date=20200217224941 }}, [http://www.minidisc.org/part_Aiwa_AMD-100.html Aiwa AMD-100] {{Wayback|url=http://www.minidisc.org/part_Aiwa_AMD-100.html |date=20200220112017 }}</ref>

*'''[[VCD|VCD]]'''：1993年索尼、松下、JVC、飞利浦公司商联合于1993年制定VCD标准，将标准命名为[[彩虹书|白皮书]]。VCD是第一个采用MPEG-1数据压缩的全数字化的激光视盘系统。VCD可以在任何兼容播放机和电脑CD-ROM上观看，主要畅销于亚洲国家，造成了许多[[盗版|盗版]]问题。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://searchstorage.techtarget.com/definition/VCD |title=VCD (video CD or video compact disc) |access-date=2013-07-16 |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125005501/https://searchstorage.techtarget.com/definition/VCD |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://searchstorage.techtarget.com/definition/White-Book |title=White Book |access-date=2013-07-16 |archive-date=2020-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021032326/https://searchstorage.techtarget.com/definition/White-Book |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.filmbug.com/dictionary/video-cd.php |title=Video CD |access-date=2013-07-16 |archive-date=2020-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924050504/https://www.filmbug.com/dictionary/video-cd.php |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Pang, Laikwan (2006). Cultural Control and Globalization in Asia: Copyright, Piracy and Cinema p.85. Routledge. ISBN 978-0415352017.</ref>

*'''[[QR码|QR码]]'''：1930年代美国的威斯汀豪斯公司的约翰·科芒德、道格拉斯·杨和哈利·斯帕克斯申请了最早的一维码或[[条码|条码]]专利。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://free-barcode.com/BarcodeHistory.htm |title=Barcode History |access-date=2017-08-21 |archive-date=2020-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200707212837/http://free-barcode.com/BarcodeHistory.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://idhistory.com/timeline.html |title=ID History Museum |access-date=2017-08-21 |archive-date=2018-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180827190056/http://idhistory.com/timeline.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://barcodeguide.seagullscientific.com/Content/BarcodeHistory.htm |title=History of Barcodes |access-date=2017-08-21 |archive-date=2020-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200619035150/https://barcodeguide.seagullscientific.com/Content/BarcodeHistory.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>1985年Cauzin公司推出世界上最早的二维码名为{{link-en|Cauzin Softstrip|Cauzin Softstrip}}，主要用于[[Apple_II|Apple II]]和[[IBM|IBM]]台式电脑。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.atarimagazines.com/compute/issue73/ibm_computing.php |title=Soffstripping |access-date=2017-08-21 |archive-date=2017-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171220172050/https://www.atarimagazines.com/compute/issue73/ibm_computing.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[1980年代|80年代]]和[[1990年代|90年代]]出现过不同的二维码，目前最为常见的二维码为[[QR码|QR码]]、[[Data_Matrix|Data Matrix]]等等，尤其是QR码；<ref>Daimi, Kevin (2017), Computer and Network Security Essentials p.208, Springer, ISBN 978-3319584232.</ref>Data Matrix为美国国际资料公司于1994年8月所研发出，主要用于零件、[[印制电路板|印制电路板]]等等；<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://files.microscan.com/_att/a3450f5d-686d-4a57-a168-aa65c5f2699d/2014-08-13_Data-Matrix-20-years.pdf |title=Microscan Celebrates 20 Years of Data Matrix Codes August 13, 2014 |access-date=2017-10-10 |archive-date=2016-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402105451/http://files.microscan.com/_att/a3450f5d-686d-4a57-a168-aa65c5f2699d/2014-08-13_Data-Matrix-20-years.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.prweb.com/releases/2014/08/prweb12091371.htm |title=Microscan Celebrates 20 Years of Data Matrix Codes |access-date=2017-10-10 |archive-date=2019-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190123200935/http://www.prweb.com/releases/2014/08/prweb12091371.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Michael, Katina, etc (2009), Innovative Automatic Identification and Location-Based Services: From Bar Codes to Chip Implants 1st Edition p.92, IGI Global, ISBN 978-1599047959.</ref>QR码为日本[[豐田|豐田]]子公司[[電裝|電裝公司]]于1994年9月所推出，在[[1990年代|90年代]]QR码只在汽车制造厂为了便于追踪零件而使用，其后QR码又投入使用于宣传广告等等，但随着拍照手机和廉价的安卓智能手机以及移动购物的逐渐普及也用于移动市场。<ref>Shen, Gang etc (2011), Advanced Research on Electronic Commerce, Web Application, and Communication p.347, Springer, ISBN 978-3642203695</ref><ref>Pasqua, Rachel and Elkin, Noah (2012), Mobile Marketing: An Hour a Day p.266, Sybex, ISBN 978-1118388440</ref>在韩国的[[乐购|乐购]]超市于2011年6月28日已使用智能手机应用扫描QR码将商品放入电子购物车。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.geek.com/geek-cetera/koreas-tesco-reinvents-grocery-shopping-with-qr-code-stores-1396025/ |title=Korea’s Tesco reinvents grocery shopping with QR-code “stores” 06.28.2011 |access-date=2017-08-22 |archive-date=2020-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200305153151/https://www.geek.com/geek-cetera/koreas-tesco-reinvents-grocery-shopping-with-qr-code-stores-1396025/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

