*'''蓝光、绿光、白光LED'''：LED (Light Emitting Diode) 是指发光二极管，1962年美国[[通用电气|通用电气]]公司一名研究人员尼克·奥隆尼亚克开发出红光LED。1972年[[孟山都|孟山都公司]]究人员乔治·克劳福德制造出黄光LED。<ref name=LemelsonMIT>{{cite web|url=http://web.mit.edu/invent/a-winners/a-holonyak.html|title=Nick Holonyak, Jr. 2004 Lemelson-MIT Prize Winner|publisher=Lemenson-MIT Program|accessdate=August 13, 2007|archive-date=2013-01-20|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DnjsIly3?url=http://web.mit.edu/invent/a-winners/a-holonyak.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.technology.gov/Medal/2002/bios/Holonyak_Craford_Dupuis.pdf|title=Brief Biography — Holonyak, Craford, Dupuis|publisher=Technology Administration|format=PDF|accessdate=May 30, 2007|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070809062214/http://www.technology.gov/Medal/2002/bios/Holonyak_Craford_Dupuis.pdf|archivedate=2007年8月9日}}</ref>1993年日亚化学公司技术员[[中村修二|中村修二]]利用半导体材料氮化镓 ([[GaN|GaN]]) 和铟氮化稼 (InGaN) 发明了蓝光LED，蓝光LED的发现导致了[[蓝雷射|蓝雷射]]的出现，具有历史意义和商业使用的价值。在蓝光LED出现之前，由于无法通过[[RGB|RGB]]系统合成白光，LED的光效、亮度也不高，LED无法应用于照明领域。因此在1995年中村修二采用铟氮化稼又发明了绿光LED，在1998年利用红、绿、蓝三种LED制成白光LED，从此绿光与白光LED研制成功，标志着LED正式进入照明领域，是LED照明发展最关键的里程碑，中村修二被誉为“蓝光、绿光、白光LED之父”，在芬兰赫尔辛基荣获2006年千年技术奖 (Millennium Technology Prize)，也是世界上最大的科技奖。<ref name="UCSB">{{Cite web |url=http://engineering.ucsb.edu/news/125/ |title=Inventor of Blue, Green, White LEDs and Blue Laser Leaves Japanese Company for U.S. University |access-date=2013-07-20 |archive-date=2017-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170929135301/https://engineering.ucsb.edu/news/125 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://dailynexus.com/2011-09-22/ucsb-professor-develops-efficient-light-displays/ |title=UCSB Professor Develops Efficient Light Displays |access-date=2013-07-20 |archive-date=2017-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170810130608/http://dailynexus.com/2011-09-22/ucsb-professor-develops-efficient-light-displays/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://muse.jhu.edu/journals/tech/summary/v049/49.2.bowers.html Brilliant! Shuji Nakamura and the Revolution in Lighting Technology (review)]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.finland.org/Public/default.aspx?contentid=178555&nodeid=40956&contentlan=2&culture=en-US |title=Millennium Prize gathered stars of science and innovation to Washington |access-date=2013-07-20 |archive-date=2017-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924094125/http://www.finland.org/Public/default.aspx?contentid=178555&nodeid=40956&contentlan=2&culture=en-US |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="mil-faq">{{Cite web |url=http://www.millenniumprize.fi/en/prize/mission/ |title=The Millennium Technology Prize: FAQ |access-date=2013-07-20 |archive-date=2011-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110928141535/http://www.millenniumprize.fi/en/prize/mission/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*'''[[蓝雷射|蓝雷射]]'''：90年代初期开始，厂商、大学和研究机构等展开了激烈的开发竞争新CD容量技术。1995年中村修二利用蓝光LED发明了蓝雷射技术，这顶技术随后用于蓝光光盘和HD DVD，是继DVD之后的新一代光盘的基础部件。<ref name="UCSB"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.electrochem.org/meetings/biannual/218/218_ecs_lecture.html |title=Current and Future Status of Nitride-based Solid State Lighting |access-date=2013-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131026115446/http://electrochem.org/meetings/biannual/218/218_ecs_lecture.html |archive-date=2013-10-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.sciencemag.org/sciencenow/2001/08/28-01.html |title=Japanese Inventor Sues Company |access-date=2013-07-20 |archive-date=2013-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130621162357/http://news.sciencemag.org/sciencenow/2001/08/28-01.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Szweda, R. (2002). Diode Laser Materials & Devices - A Worldwide Market & Technology Overview to 2005. Elsevier Science. ISBN 978-1856173865.</ref>

