*'''[[手机|拍照手机]]'''：[[夏普|夏普]]于2000年11月在日本推出了全球第一款拍照手机{{link-en|J-SH04|J-SH04}}，手机采用11万像素的CMOS摄像头，256色显示屏，仅重74克。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2023689_2023708_2023648,00.html |title=Sharp J-SH04 - All-TIME 100 Gadgets - TIME |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2013-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130817075919/http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2023689_2023708_2023648,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Sharp J-SH04: World’s First Ever Phone With Integrated Camera|url=http://gadgetizor.com/sharp-j-sh04-worlds-first-ever-phone-with-integrated-camera-pictures-2001/5482/|publisher=Digitizor Media & Web, Inc.|accessdate=26 August 2012|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109041208/https://gadgetizor.com/sharp-j-sh04-worlds-first-ever-phone-with-integrated-camera-pictures-2001/5482/|dead-url=no}}</ref>也有认为韩国三星于同年6月发布的SCH-V200才是第一款拍照手机，不过有分析家认为SCH-V200只能算是拍照手机的半成品，所以严格来说不能算是真正的拍照手机。<ref>{{cite web|title=Sharp J-SH04 – first to discover the consumer love affair with the camera phone (2001)|url=http://www.gsmhistory.com/vintage-mobiles/#sharp_sh04_2001|publisher=Stephen Temple|accessdate=6 April 2013|archive-date=2016-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160126051916/http://www.gsmhistory.com/vintage-mobiles/#sharp_sh04_2001|dead-url=no}}</ref>法国数学家{{link-en|菲利普·康|Philippe Kahn}}曾于1997年尝试使用一台{{link-en|摩托罗拉StarTAC|Motorola StarTAC}}翻盖型手机上传他新生儿照片，但这并不算世界上首款拍照手机，因为这张新生儿的照片实际是用卡西欧的QV-10数码相机拍下，通过他手中的卡西欧相机—东芝电脑笔记本—摩托罗拉手机—几条电缆的互联，实现了这一从拍摄到上传的过程，这是第一张利用卡西欧QV-10相机拍摄并通过手机无线上传至网站的照片，也是最早的即时照片分享的例子，但却不是通过拍照手机或手机内置摄像头拍摄的第一张照片。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://100photos.time.com/photos/philippe-kahn-first-cell-phone-picture |title=First Cell-Phone Picture {{!}} 100 Photographs {{!}} The Most Influential Images of All Time |access-date=2017-10-25 |archive-date=2020-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101022448/http://100photos.time.com/photos/philippe-kahn-first-cell-phone-picture |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://d3ao8sz5crj5i0.cloudfront.net/philippe-kahn-cell-phone-camera_0.jpg |title=A digital camera connected to his flip-top cell phone, synched by a few lines of code he'd written on his laptop |access-date=2017-10-25 |archive-date=2020-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827230557/http://d3ao8sz5crj5i0.cloudfront.net/philippe-kahn-cell-phone-camera_0.jpg |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://spectrum.ieee.org/view-from-the-valley/consumer-electronics/audiovideo/happy-birthday-camera-phone-your-papa-is-very-proud-of-you |title=Happy Birthday, Camera Phone! Your Papa Is Very Proud of You - IEEE Spectrum |access-date=2017-10-25 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112000050/https://spectrum.ieee.org/view-from-the-valley/consumer-electronics/audiovideo/happy-birthday-camera-phone-your-papa-is-very-proud-of-you |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mashable.com/2012/03/06/philippe-kahn-camera-phone/#KPzPGppVBZqG |title=Meet the Man Behind the Very First Camera Phone |access-date=2017-10-25 |archive-date=2021-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112200636/https://mashable.com/2012/03/06/philippe-kahn-camera-phone/#KPzPGppVBZqG |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2001/07/09/business/technology-lightsurf-piggybacks-a-tiny-camera-on-a-cell-phone.html |title=TECHNOLOGY; LightSurf Piggybacks a Tiny Camera on a Cell Phone |access-date=2017-10-25 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112015108/https://www.nytimes.com/2001/07/09/business/technology-lightsurf-piggybacks-a-tiny-camera-on-a-cell-phone.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[奧林巴斯|奧林巴斯]]公司曾于1994年推出过世界上第一款可上传的数码相机，该数码相机能通过手机无线或拨号上网上传照片至电脑，在[[京瓷|京瓷]]于1999年、夏普2000年推出的两款手机之前，没有一部手机有内置摄像头。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cnet.com/news/who-invented-the-camera-phone-it-depends/ |title=Who invented the camera phone? It depends - CNET |access-date=2017-10-25 |archive-date=2017-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171026054301/https://www.cnet.com/news/who-invented-the-camera-phone-it-depends/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.digicamhistory.com/1994.html |title=digicamhistory 1994 |access-date=2017-10-25 |archive-date=2020-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200706184037/http://www.digicamhistory.com/1994.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>据2014年韩国三星的调查，全球智能手机用户中有92％使用手机拍照和发文字信息信，其次有84％使用手机浏览互联网。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://petapixel.com/2015/02/12/importance-cameras-smartphone-war/ |title=The Importance of Cameras in the Smartphone War |access-date=2015-05-18 |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129180824/https://petapixel.com/2015/02/12/importance-cameras-smartphone-war/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>摄像、上网和触屏功能无疑是智能手机重要组成分，[[Sprint|Sprint]]在2003年3月17日发布基于[[Windows_Mobile|Windows Mobile]] ([[Pocket_PC|Pocket PC]] 2002手机版) 的三星SPH-i700和[[日立製作所|日立]]G1000都有内置摄像头，两款手机都配有[[十字键|D-Pad]]和[[QWERTY键盘|QWERTY键盘]]并非全触屏手机。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tech-insider.org/mobile/research/2003/0313-a.html |title=Sprint introduces two Vision(SM)-Capable PCS Phones with Windows Powered Pocket PC software featuring high-speed Web browsing, wireless email, built-in cameras and Windows Media Player |access-date=2015-05-19 |archive-date=2017-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170114020558/http://tech-insider.org/mobile/research/2003/0313-a.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.phonearena.com/phones/Samsung-SPH-i700_id433 |title=Samsung SPH-i700 |access-date=2015-05-19 |archive-date=2019-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190131041813/https://www.phonearena.com/phones/Samsung-SPH-i700_id433 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.phonearena.com/phones/Hitachi-G1000_id581 |title=Hitachi G1000 |access-date=2015-05-19 |archive-date=2020-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201161447/https://www.phonearena.com/phones/Hitachi-G1000_id581 |dead-url=no }}</ref>美国[[IBM|IBM]]在1994年8月16日推出的[[IBM_Simon|IBM Simon]]虽为智能手机始祖，该手机没有内置摄像头，且由于当时移动互联网并不主流，也没有上网功能，发送和接收邮件需经电缆连接一台电脑，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-2725934/First-smartphone-display.html |title=Meet Simon, the world's first smartphone that could fax, draw and even had 'apps': IBM's mobile celebrates its 20th birthday |access-date=2015-05-19 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111215143/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-2725934/First-smartphone-display.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/mobile-phones/11037661/Smartphone-at-20-IBM-Simon-to-iPhone-6.html |title=Smartphone at 20: IBM Simon to iPhone 6 |access-date=2016-05-29 |archive-date=2020-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201012034857/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/mobile-phones/11037661/Smartphone-at-20-IBM-Simon-to-iPhone-6.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>在2007年6月29日[[IPhone_(第一代)|iPhone 2G]]上市前没有一款手机同时具有全触屏、摄像和上网这三项功能。[[谷歌|谷歌]]于2007年11月发布的安卓原型机HTC EXCA 300 (Sooner)，并没有触屏功能，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://9to5google.com/2012/05/05/2007s-pre-m3-version-of-android-the-google-sooner/ |title=2007’s pre-M3 version of Android; the Google Sooner |access-date=2015-05-18 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112020747/https://9to5google.com/2012/05/05/2007s-pre-m3-version-of-android-the-google-sooner/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>直到2009年4月27日[[HTC_Magic|HTC Magic]]上市前为止，全球市场上没有任何一部全触屏安卓手机。<ref>[http://www.techfragments.com/nl/394/android-based-htc-magic-smartphone-with-touchscreen-keyboard/ Android Based HTC Magic Smartphone with Touchscreen Keyboard]{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

*'''[[3G|3G移动互联网、3G手机]]'''：日本[[NTT_DOCOMO|NTT DOCOMO]]于2001年10月1日提供全球第一项3G移动互联网服务，该服务基于[[W-CDMA|W-CDMA]]技术，并推出首批3G手机，首批推出的3G手机共3种款式，这3款手机分别为[[松下|松下]]P2101V、P2401和[[日本电气|日本电气]]N2001，NTT DOCOMO为3G手机用户提供的服务命名为[[FOMA|FOMA]]，意为移动多媒体自由接入。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.computerweekly.com/news/2240042558/First-commercial-3G-service-launched-in-Japan |title=First commercial 3G service launched in Japan |access-date=2015-05-18 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126021559/https://www.computerweekly.com/news/2240042558/First-commercial-3G-service-launched-in-Japan |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/cyber/wireless/2001/09/28/3g-first-phones.htm |title=First look: First third-generation phones |access-date=2015-05-18 |archive-date=2018-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181201001723/https://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/cyber/wireless/2001/09/28/3g-first-phones.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2001/TECH/ptech/10/02/docomo.3G.idg/index.html |title=DoCoMo launches Third-Generation Service--at last |access-date=2015-05-18 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305100217/http://edition.cnn.com/2001/TECH/ptech/10/02/docomo.3G.idg/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://business.china.com/zh_cn/news1/mtel/1926/20011019/10131429.html |title=日本推出首批3G手机 |access-date=2015-05-18 |archive-date=2015-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150519050925/http://business.china.com/zh_cn/news1/mtel/1926/20011019/10131429.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>在日本以外最早推出3G移动互联网服务的为挪威Telenor和Netcom通讯公司，于2001年12月推出，但是没有推出任何3G手机。韩国[[SK电讯|SK电讯]]分别在2000年10月1日和2002年1月28日推出了CDMA2000 1x ([[2.5G|2.5G]]) 和 1xEV ([[3G|3G]]) 移动互联网服务，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.itu.int/osg/imt-project/Subdirectories_links/implementation.html |title=IMT-2000 IMPLEMENTATION |access-date=2015-05-19 |archive-date=2017-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170107031149/http://www.itu.int/osg/imt-project/Subdirectories_links/implementation.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.itu.int/itunews/issue/2003/06/thirdgeneration.html |title=THE EVOLUTION TO 3G MOBILE — STATUS REPORT |access-date=2015-05-19 |archive-date=2019-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913152440/https://www.itu.int/itunews/issue/2003/06/thirdgeneration.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.3g.co.uk/PR/April2002/3273.htm |title=CDMA2000 1x EV-DO is fast enough to be 3G |access-date=2015-05-19 |archive-date=2015-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150520172442/http://www.3g.co.uk/PR/April2002/3273.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Mallick, Martyn (2003), Mobile and Wireless Design Essentials, ISBN 978-0471466284, pg.78-9.</ref>三星于2010年9月30日推出第一款[[長期演進技術|LTE]]手机SCH-r900，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.engadget.com/2010/03/24/motropcs-bringing-lte-to-las-vegas-this-year-samsung-doing-infr/ |title=MetroPCS bringing LTE to Las Vegas this year, Samsung doing infrastructure and first LTE handset: the SCH-r900 |access-date=2015-05-18 |archive-date=2017-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924142059/https://www.engadget.com/2010/03/24/motropcs-bringing-lte-to-las-vegas-this-year-samsung-doing-infr/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2369973,00.asp |title=Samsung Craft SCH-R900 (MetroPCS) |access-date=2015-05-18 |archive-date=2017-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924141939/https://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2369973,00.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>并于2013年6月25日推出全球第一款LTE-A ([[4G|4G]]) 手机[[三星Galaxy_S4|Galaxy S4]] I9506。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.androidcentral.com/samsung-galaxy-s4-lte-announced-becomes-world-s-first-lte-advanced-phone |title=Samsung Galaxy S4 LTE-A announced as world's first LTE-Advanced smartphone |access-date=2015-05-18 |archive-date=2017-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170814215815/https://www.androidcentral.com/samsung-galaxy-s4-lte-announced-becomes-world-s-first-lte-advanced-phone |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cnet.com/news/sk-telecom-launches-worlds-first-lte-advanced-network/ |title=SK Telecom launches world's first LTE-Advanced network |access-date=2015-05-18 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111165533/https://www.cnet.com/news/sk-telecom-launches-worlds-first-lte-advanced-network/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*'''[[近場通訊|NFC]]'''：NFC最早于2002年9月5日为[[索尼|索尼]]公司和[[飞利浦|飞利浦]]公司共同开始研制开发，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.sony.net/SonyInfo/News/Press_Archive/200209/02-0905E/ |title=PHILIPS AND SONY ANNOUNCE STRATEGIC COOPERATION TO DEFINE NEXT GENERATION NEAR FIELD RADIO-FREQUENCY COMMUNICATIONS |access-date=2017-08-21 |archive-date=2020-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022185620/https://www.sony.net/SonyInfo/News/Press_Archive/200209/02-0905E/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>并于2004年3月18日与[[诺基亚|诺基亚]]公司在[[德国|德国]][[漢諾威|漢諾威]]正式宣布成立NFC论坛。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://nfc-forum.org/newsroom/nokia-philips-and-sony-establish-the-near-field-communication-nfc-forum/ |title=Nokia, Philips And Sony Establish The Near Field Communication (NFC) Forum |access-date=2017-08-21 |archive-date=2018-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180708221434/https://nfc-forum.org/newsroom/nokia-philips-and-sony-establish-the-near-field-communication-nfc-forum/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>诺基亚公司于2007年1月8日在[[消費電子展|消費電子展]]公布全球第一款搭载NFC技术的手机{{link-en|诺基亚6131|Nokia 6131}}；<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.pocket-lint.com/news/79059-nokia-6131-nfc-n76-n93i |title=CES 2007: Nokia launches 6131 NFC, N76, and N93i |access-date=2017-08-21 |archive-date=2017-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822053725/http://www.pocket-lint.com/news/79059-nokia-6131-nfc-n76-n93i |dead-url=no }}</ref>最早搭载NFC技术的[[安卓|安卓]]智能手机为[[谷歌|谷歌]]和[[三星集團|三星]]于2010年12月7日推出的[[Nexus_S|Nexus S]]；最早支持NFC技术的苹果智能手机为2014年推出的[[iPhone_6|iPhone 6]]系列。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.nfcworld.com/2014/09/09/331412/iphone-6-come-nfc/ |title=iPhone 6 to ship with NFC and support for Apple Pay mobile payments |access-date=2017-08-22 |archive-date=2018-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180906221227/https://www.nfcworld.com/2014/09/09/331412/iphone-6-come-nfc/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>苹果于2014年10月20日推出基于NFC技术的移动支付和电子现金服务的[[Apple_Pay|Apple Pay]]；三星于2015年8月20日推出[[Samsung_Pay|Samsung Pay]]服务；谷歌于2015年9月11日推出[[Google_Pay|Google Pay]]服务。

*'''[[行動支付|移动互联网支付]]'''：最早的互联网支付或网络支付出现于1994年8月11日的美国，第一笔安全交易为[[史汀|史汀]]的{{link-en|Ten Summoner's Tales|Ten Summoner's Tales}}CD，加上运费售价12.48美元。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cnet.com/news/e-commerce-turns-10/ |title=E-commerce turns 10 |access-date=2017-08-22 |archive-date=2017-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215171314/https://www.cnet.com/news/e-commerce-turns-10/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>移动支付最早出现在1997年的[[芬兰|芬兰]][[赫尔辛基|赫尔辛基]]，由芬兰[[北欧银行|梅丽塔银行]]通过用手机的[[短信|SMS]]完成[[自动售货机|自动售货机]]付款购买[[可口可乐|可口可乐]]，<ref name="Fleishman">Fleishman, Daniel (1996), Fare Policies, Structures, and Technologies p.41-45, National Academy Press, ISBN 978-0309057134.</ref>1998年出现最早的下载商品，为芬兰{{link-en|Radiolinja|Radiolinja}}电信公司推出的手机铃声下载服务，通过用手机的SMS进行付款。<ref>Naha, Abhi etc (2012), Essentials of Mobile Handset Design p.18, Cambridge University Press, ISBN 978-1107610446</ref>但这些例子是通过SMS无需连接[[互联网|移动互联网]]，最早的移动互联网支付出现于日本，基于[[NTT_DOCOMO|NTT DOCOMO]]提供的[[i-mode|i-mode]]电子商务，用于支付地铁车票、演唱会入门票等等。<ref name="Fleishman"/>

*'''[[手表|MP3手表]]'''：日本[[卡西歐|卡西歐]]公司于2000年在[[消費電子展|消費電子展]]推出世界上第一个能播放MP3的数手表、第一个音乐播放器手表卡西歐WMP-1V，卡西歐WMP-1V于2000年3月30日上市。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://world.casio.com/corporate/history/chapter04/ |title=Casio History 2000- |access-date=2017-09-24 |archive-date=2020-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130144718/https://world.casio.com/corporate/history/chapter04/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gadgetcentral.com/casiomp3_intro.htm |title=Casio's "Music on a Wrist" MP3 Player MAR-30-2000 |access-date=2017-09-24 |archive-date=2020-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920235729/http://www.gadgetcentral.com/casiomp3_intro.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.neoseeker.com/Articles/Hardware/Reviews/casio_wmp1v/ |title=Casio WMP-1V MP3 Audio Wrist Watch Review |access-date=2017-09-24 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109041215/https://www.neoseeker.com/Articles/Hardware/Reviews/casio_wmp1v/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*'''智能机器人'''：2000年10月31日本田公司发布[[ASIMO|ASIMO]]，是Advanced Step Innovative Mobility (高级步行创新移动机器人) 的缩写，这是世界上第一个AI或智能机器人。ASIMO身高1.2米，体重43公斤，肩关节的高度为9.1米，大腿的高度为6.1米，肩膀厚度为4.4米，共26个自由度关节。ASIMO的[[三維晶片|三维处理器]]为本田独自开发，配备了智能实时自由步行技术 (Intelligent Real-Time Flexible Walking Technology)，简称I-Walk。<ref name="Masato"/><ref>{{cite news|last=Hiratsuka|first=Mark|title=Honda Creates 3D CPU|url=http://www.digitalworldtokyo.com/index.php/digital_tokyo/articles/honda_creates_3d_cpu_to_power_super_asimo|newspaper=Digital World Tokyo|date=30 January 2008|accessdate=27 July 2011|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031231139/http://www.digitalworldtokyo.com/index.php/digital_tokyo/articles/honda_creates_3d_cpu_to_power_super_asimo/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://science.howstuffworks.com/asimo.htm |title=How ASIMO Works |access-date=2013-07-19 |archive-date=2020-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201092421/https://science.howstuffworks.com/asimo.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.21stcentury.co.uk/robotics/honda_asimo_robot.asp |title=Honda ASIMO Robot |access-date=2013-07-19 |archive-date=2014-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223164622/http://www.21stcentury.co.uk/robotics/honda_asimo_robot.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>ASIMO第一次在2000年11月24横滨市举办的机器人展览会 (ROBODEX) 上展出，索尼公司生产的智能机器狗[[AIBO|AIBO]]均参加了展出。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.robots.org/Japan/Robodex%20PCWatch%20Japan%20Translate.htm |title=New robots such as Sony and HONDA general open it to the public |access-date=2013-07-19 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304212036/http://www.robots.org/Japan/Robodex%20PCWatch%20Japan%20Translate.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>2005版的ASIMO，除具备了行走功能与各种人类肢体动作之外，还增强了人工智能，可以预先设定动作，还能依据人类的声音、手势等指令，来从事相应动作，此外，他还具备了基本的记忆与辨识能力。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://world.honda.com/news/2007/c071211Enabling-Multiple-ASIMO-to-Work/ |title=Honda Develops Intelligence Technologies Enabling Multiple ASIMO Robots to Work Together in Coordination |access-date=2013-07-19 |archive-date=2013-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130423180929/http://world.honda.com/news/2007/c071211Enabling-Multiple-ASIMO-to-Work/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://asimo.honda.com/asimo-intelligence/ |title=ASIMO's Intelligence |access-date=2013-07-19 |archive-date=2020-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200129231338/https://asimo.honda.com/asimo-intelligence/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/8878257/Artificial-intelligence-robot-which-can-help-round-the-home-is-unveiled.html |title=Artificial intelligence robot which can help round the home is unveiled |access-date=2013-07-19 |archive-date=2017-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170710143252/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/8878257/Artificial-intelligence-robot-which-can-help-round-the-home-is-unveiled.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2011年版全身自由关节增加至57处，跑步速度由6公里每小时提高为9公里每小时。<ref>{{cite news|last=|first=|title=Honda Unveils All-new ASIMO with Significant Advancements “Honda Robotics” established as new collective name to represent Honda robotics research and all product applications|url=http://world.honda.com/news/2011/c111108All-new-ASIMO/index.html|accessdate=6 May 2013|publisher=Honda Worldwide site|date=8 November 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130628062802/http://world.honda.com/news/2011/c111108All-new-ASIMO/index.html|archivedate=2013年6月28日}}</ref>载至2007年为止，已有46台ASIMO被产出，每年雇用费用为166,000美元。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.robotsandcomputers.com/robots/asimo.htm |title=Asimo |access-date=2013-07-19 |archive-date=2020-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200121061240/http://www.robotsandcomputers.com/robots/asimo.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

