archive-date=2013-05-21 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6GnALqMNl?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/4714135.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*'''[[HD_DVD|HD DVD]]'''：2002年8月29日[[东芝|东芝]]和[[NEC|NEC]]公司向[[DVD论坛|DVD论坛]]提交了新一代DVD光盘规格，当时的名字为Advanced Optical Disc，简称AOD，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/id,104570-page,1/article.html |title=Toshiba, NEC Share Details of Blue-Laser Storage |accessdate=October 18, 2007 |author= |date=August 29, 2002 |work=pcworld.com |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071106000320/http://www.pcworld.com/article/id%2C104570-page%2C1/article.html |archivedate=2007年11月6日 }}</ref>2003年11月19日DVD论坛投票通过将光盘改名为HD DVD，HD DVD成为DVD配合[[高清晰度电视|高清电视]]的下一代产品。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://disc-formats.guidechart.com/hd-dvd.html |title=Disc Formats HD DVD |access-date=2013-07-18 |archive-date=2017-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170427151739/http://disc-formats.guidechart.com/hd-dvd.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2004年9月27日[[东芝|东芝]]、[[NEC|NEC]]、[[三洋|三洋]]和Memory-Tech公司组成的[[HD_DVD推广协会|HD DVD推广协会]]负责推广HD DVD。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.cnet.com/HD-DVD-group-forms-promotion-unit/2110-1041_3-5384389.html |title=HD-DVD group forms promotion unit |access-date=2013-07-18 |archive-date=2012-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121104003829/http://news.cnet.com/HD-DVD-group-forms-promotion-unit/2110-1041_3-5384389.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>HD DVD与蓝光两种格式的厚度不同，它们互不兼容，统一标准需要某一方放弃自己的格式，而这是一种双方都不愿接受的选择，因此展开类似于70、80年代[[VHS|VHS]]和[[Beta|Beta]]的格式之战。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.engadget.com/2005/09/19/blu-ray-vs-hd-dvd-state-of-the-s-union-s-division/ |title=Blu-ray vs HD DVD: State of the Division |access-date=2013-07-18 |archive-date=2019-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191017050809/https://www.engadget.com/2005/09/19/blu-ray-vs-hd-dvd-state-of-the-s-union-s-division/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=Dranove |first=David |coauthors=Neil Gandal |title=Surviving a Standards War: Lessons Learned from the Life and Death of DIVX |publisher=Idea Group Inc.}}</ref>2008年1月4日[[华纳兄弟|华纳兄弟]]电影公司宣布脱离HD DVD阵营，并且开始停止发布HD-DVD光盘，往后只支持蓝光光盘作为影碟格式。东芝公司终在2008年2月19日正式宣布将终止HD DVD事业。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.timewarner.com/corp/newsroom/pr/0,20812,1700383,00.html |title=Warner Bros. Entertainment to Release its High-Definition DVD Titles Exclusively in the Blu-Ray Disc Format Beginning Later This Year |accessdate=2008-01-07 |date=January 4, 2008 |publisher=Time Warner |archive-date=2008-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080513085506/http://www.timewarner.com/corp/newsroom/pr/0,20812,1700383,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author=Scott Snowden | coauthors=Tony Smith | title=Official: Toshiba discontinues HD DVD | date=19 February 2008 | publisher= | url=http://www.reghardware.co.uk/2008/02/19/tosh_drops_hd_dvd/ | work=reghardware | pages= | accessdate=2008-02-19 | language= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080220010549/http://www.reghardware.co.uk/2008/02/19/tosh_drops_hd_dvd/ | archive-date=2008-02-20 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>

